mens, Abyss (Abyss) Chakram, and the energy and aid of 5 Fatesenders.  A list of failed locations attempted in the forging is present, each location scratched out until the final location of \"Mystic Tunnel\" is circled and underlined 3 times.  ','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1453533,5877,13437953,0,0,'Cell Key',0,17,25,-716,-12514,'A long key made of bone with intricate black engravings on the handle.','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1652361,5301,13437953,0,0,'KoES Crest',0,17,25,-661,-12057,'A crest of the umbric stronghold.  It has been fragmented into several parts.','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1627136,4060088693,13437953,0,0,'S',0,23,4,424,-8799,'A square stone tablet.  In the middle of the tablet, is a large engraving of the letter: S','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1408761,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Sanc Res\'ing IV',0,41,11,-5809,-1890,'Now at the end, the last two storm in from sanctuary and evoke that same art on himself and his hero. Now unable to fight the two watch as the male dreamer is soon collapsed. Now Mortyki finding his strength returning jumps back into the fight but the inevitable prevails and they two fall. As he collapses though, there was something else. . . was that the fell art?. . ','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1408696,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Sanc Res\'ing',0,41,11,-5821,-1940,'As Mortyki opened his eyes, he recognized the Dark Awakening. Finally, he thought, now we can finish this. In the next room he saw a male dreamer and dozens of his brethren. Mortyki stepped into the circle and was showered with energies, same as the others. Now prepared, their leader roars in triumph and the male dreamer points onward. \r\nThey charge. They find their would be victims in Chasm of Souls. Six of them to count. Strangely they all have circles. Two of them are golden, the others shine emerald.','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1408728,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Sanc Res\'ing II',0,41,11,-5822,-1922,'The dreamers scatter.\r\nOnly the two with golden circles stay to fight, the rest haphazardly break for sanctuary. Thirty against two, this will be a feast. As the onslaught begins, Mortyki and his brethren pound the two dreamers with fire. The two lash out blindly amongst the ranks but something is wrong.\r\nAll the fire isn\'t enough to overcome the restorers hiding in sanctuary. A small detachment breaks rank to guard the sanctuary. After only a moments time, two of the dreamers from sanctuary burst in.','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(1408760,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Sanc Res\'ing III',0,41,11,-5817,-1905,'Simultaneously they evoke something on two of us. Those two stop fighting for some strange reason and then two more fall to the assualt of the four. This cycle continues and Mortyki howls in rage and anguish as their numbers thin. \r\nSix datoken that Mortyki grew up with turn and flee. He spits in disgust and turns back to the fight. He slings chak after chak in a futile effort. With so many restores the effort is in vain.\r\nNow standing alone with the male dreamer and their datoken hero.','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(8941781,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,9,4046,-10276,'Isis atsila-jsopi waqa mu um attakjsks!!! Ktak atsila-jsopi en kapuxtra eovoc u kipotik eovoc aw guasata.','2016-05-10 17:08:29'),(1428135,437,13437953,0,0,'Half-Egg Basin',0,47,6,-2064,4931,'The bottom part of an egg with several cracks in the surface, the top half has been removed.  In the bottom of the basin is a dried goo and ash mixture.  ','2015-10-10 16:27:44'),(12719307,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,50,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:28'),(1516663,101451833,33555041,197122,0,'The Knowing Glass',0,22,22,-8846,-7724,'A globe that resonates when you pick it up and gaze into its cloudy center. It is wrapped in a protective sheet of irridescence and as you turn it over in your hand, runes appear and then disappear. If concentrated on, the Knowing Glass will clear and show you aspects of what you are wishing to see. There is a large webbed crack in the surface of the inner