15 01:56:52'),(7808106,554174948,3070,2113929216,40,'~ Reignite ~',0,41,11,-7062,-2420,'The flame of our city sputters, leaving only long shadows in the wake of its former self. Chaos accretes amongst those viscous dreamers who dawdle in the halls of our homes and our Threshold; rekindle or we will be naught but ashes. Ignite and fight fire with fire.','2015-12-16 21:19:48'),(8090068,50336885,13437964,0,0,'Crest',0,18,8,8243,2212,'A house crest bearing the Gathering of the Entranced symbol is cracked and very fragile; as though too much handling could cause it to disintigrate. ','2016-01-23 03:23:16'),(8935894,4077390308,3070,4261412864,41,'Water Painting',0,47,13,-7999,-383,'A simple painting, done on a small post stamp sized piece of paper.  The painting is of a mountain ledge of black rock overlooking a pale orange sky, with brilliant purple and crimson aurura\'s high above.  Hidden in the aurura are hints of peoples faces, isolated from each other but with pale bolts flashing between them.  A green terrace with a worn flagstone path winds its way just barely visible under the ledge.  The style is primitive, with almost agressive brush strokes.','2016-05-10 02:55:38'),(9075598,2265450980,3070,4261412864,41,'Calenture: Essence',0,47,2,-2884,-600,'House Calenture banishes to ensure the safest possible removal of the mares chaotic energy, and harnessing what\'s left.  While imprisoning traps all of the energy in the city, and draining pulls it into the avatar of the drainer.  Cleansing is also risky as it is difficult to ensure that the tainted energy has been adequately neutralized.','2016-05-28 04:20:42'),(8104492,4309,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag',0,22,22,-10251,-6893,'','2016-01-25 03:57:33'),(8005452,4144499176,9374511,419430400,2562087,'Misdirection-Learn',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'I don\'t like writing Misdirection tasks. Write me two different tasks relating to Misdirection so that I can steal them sometime. Also, collapse a Bogrom with your Blade while only moving backwards. Have a witness handy. Share all the details with me.','2016-01-12 02:38:00'),(7979716,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Invis Pad Locations',0,41,11,-6837,-2028,'Harrow Glades- West Glade\r\nCenotaph of Dread- Cistern of Torture\r\nChasm of Souls- The Little Cave\r\nLost Caves- The Lair of Teng\r\n(2)Caudal Rift- Horron\'s Lair\r\n(2)Citadel- Approach of Markosh, Shrine of Relminus the Blind','2016-01-08 16:29:30'),(10205684,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,9351,-4641,'','2016-10-14 02:35:42'),(7979622,2684881380,3070,402653184,39,'Kailee\'s Project',0,41,18,-8990,252,'Please leave these be for now. I am working on a task for the teacher halls. They are only here temporarily.','2016-01-08 16:16:35'),(7989790,2148010468,3070,4261412864,41,'ID Curse (5)',0,41,5,231,-6197,'Albestor carried on in hiding teaching a select few of his followers to pass on the art of Identify Curse. Eventually, Albestor confronted the DreamStrike Masters and the Entropy Coalition in hopes of bringing peace at the height of the DreamStrike Wars, and was subsequently DreamStruck in fear of bringing about a following similar to that of DiBauda. ','2016-01-10 02:49:34'),(10205682,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,10001,-5402,'','2016-10-14 02:35:34'),(10205683,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,8843,-2233,'','2016-10-14 02:35:38'),(10205681,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7816,-3386,'','2016-10-14 02:35:28'),(10205680,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,10901,-4446,'','2016-10-14 02:35:21'),(7989758,2148010468,3070,4261412864,41,'ID Curse (4)',0,41,5,225,-6209,'He attempted to gather all those that he had befriended and helped in the past to help aid his cause to fight the DreamStrike Masters and the Entropy Coalition, believing one group or the other would bring the dream under their sway and have total subjection of the dream before the end, or until they destroyed the dream. The DreamStrike Masters, fearing DiBauda and his following attacked and were able to remove DiBauda and 3 of his followers. The 4th, Albestor, went into hiding.\r\n','2016-01-10 02:48:54'),(7989757,2148010468,3070,4261412864,41,'ID Curse (3)',0,41,5,220,-6217,'These 4 dreamers were known as Lorac, the creator of Purify, Morden, the creator of Protection, and Cybele, the creator of Identify and a little known dreamer named Albestor who is still forgotten in the dream, though his deeds for both the dream, and for illuminates are both extensive and far-reaching. DiBauda gathered these 4 apprentices before the height of the DreamStrike Wars opposing both the DreamStrike Masters AND the Entropy Coalition.\r\n','2016-01-10 02:48:22'),(7989756,2148010468,3070,4261412864,41,'ID Curse (2)',0,41,5,217,-6228,'DiBauda was a DreamSeer of great influence because of this, and was feared by those who wanted others to succumb to their wills because DiBauda knew what dreamers held in their hearts, no matter how secret they kept it from others. DiBauda had discovered a way of transferring this ability to his use of insight, and was able to teach dreamers the ability to detect the burdens others bared in order to help them. He held himself to 4 apprentices.','2016-01-10 02:47:44'),(7989755,2148010468,3070,4261412864,41,'ID Curse (1)',0,41,5,214,-6242,'Identify Curse was an art created before the great loss by a dreamer named DiBauda. This dreamer came into the dream just before the beginning of the DreamStrike Wars, and was an empath in his shard. DiBauda was able to carry over his ability to dream as an empath, and was able to feel what others were feeling. His ability to give the prognosis to almost any problem was unrivaled, and knew for the most part what dreamers were feeling, because he himself was able to feel it.\r\n','2016-01-10 02:47:09'),(8005515,1124600292,5442558,452984832,2562090,'Kailee - Terror 10',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'Take steps to attempt to identify who the next big terror in the City will be, as it seems the Consortium has withered away. Additionally, begin to forumlate plans of actions for those terrors. Consult with others who may have ideas. Provide at least 3 potential big bad guys.','2016-01-12 02:46:30'),(8012419,50334069,13437953,0,0,'1 or L',0,23,2,591,-2824,'A square stone tablet.  In the middle of the tablet is a large engraving of the letter: \"L\" or if turned upside down the number \"1\"','2016-01-13 03:03:57'),(8104451,6165,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag',0,22,22,-10032,-6587,'','2016-01-25 03:45:23'),(8090036,855643957,13437976,0,0,'Key',0,18,8,8483,2644,'This appears to be a very simple key; free of flaws with a single word etched into it. \"Vault\".','2016-01-23 03:21:50'),(8104524,4437,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag HC',0,17,25,-200,-13084,'','2016-01-25 03:58:10'),(12717662,151259208,66330,10808,0,'Plum Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717661,2566981576,537068053,0,0,'Plum Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717660,133312,185272321,3,0,'Chalk Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717659,3053520840,855769625,0,0,'Cyan Sand Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(8175682,71289,4093641416,0,0,'Loose Brick',0,22,22,-9317,-7813,'A yellow-orange brick, similair to the ones of the PoR facade.  A draining aura surrounds the brick, slowly pulling any nearby dreamsoul towards it.  ','2016-02-03 04:01:30'),(8104450,6037,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag',0,22,22,-10116,-6594,'','2016-01-25 03:44:38'),(8175918,855706617,471074047,0,0,'Dynroth\'s Staff',0,18,8,8433,2105,'A long golden staff encrusted with rubies, sapphires, and other rare gemstones.  It’s form fades in and out of visibility, as if it is in more than one plane of existence.  The gold at the top of the staff spirals up clockwise in 5 different points, forming a large golden sphere.  Inside the sphere, a glowing azure orb of pure elementium hovers.','2016-02-03 04:53:10'),(8090220,150998005,13437987,0,0,'Spectacular Staff',0,17,22,6729,5278,'A jeweled staff with an intricate design swirling from top to bottom. The tip of the staff is set with an enormous resilient jewel and the entire staff crackles with pink bursts of lightning. It radiates positive energy.','2016-01-23 03:51:11'),(8090218,285214005,13437953,0,0,'Soul Essence',0,18,8,8180,2393,'A soul essence of undetermined origin.','2016-01-23 03:49:46'),(8104382,5973,13437953,0,0,'Ceremony Flag',0,22,22,-10037,-6502,'','2016-01-25 03:33:05'),(8104383,6037,13437953,0,0,'Ceremony Flag',0,22,22,-10028,-6341,'','2016-01-25 03:34:03'),(8104490,69721,1056965121,0,0,'Renewal Flag AoE',0,22,22,-10125,-6895,'','2016-01-25 03:54:46'),(8104317,6165,13437953,0,0,'Ceremony Flag',0,22,22,-10026,-6267,'','2016-01-25 03:30:32'),(8104449,5973,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag',0,22,22,-10323,-6588,'','2016-01-25 03:44:03'),(8104448,5973,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Flag',0,22,22,-10205,-6593,'','2016-01-25 03:43:40'),(8104484,4565,13437953,0,0,'Renewal Banner',0,22,22,-10188,-6894,'','2016-01-25 03:48:53'),(8356955,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Lucid Plates',0,41,20,3685,1005,'The Lucidic plates created in the art of Enfeeblement attach to the legs of a target, weighing them down, slowing their movement. They slowly decay, oozing down the legs -- a further deterrant to movement, before falling apart entirely, and freeing the legs. ','2016-02-26 09:33:19'),(8356954,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Plans: 1.0',0,41,20,3705,1003,'Step 1: Work with fellow Dreamers to forge decaying Lucid plates.\r\nStep 2: Patternize the creation of these Lucid Plates. \r\nStep 3: Introduce the pattern to the Dream City as a Lucid Art. ','2016-02-26 09:32:15'),(10764416,526867,2112356609,1537047,1537792,'Ward',0,24,30,-4297,-1697,'','2016-12-21 05:41:39'),(8722111,526820,3070,4026531840,40,'Codex of Spheres',0,47,12,5759,6569,'Thunderman is undergoing the transformation of focus and is exempt from sphere tasks. He will need the proper supports for spheres 4 and above before he can be granted the sphere. **A**','2016-04-13 03:21:59'),(12718258,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,23,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:01'),(12718252,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,23,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:01'),(12718251,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,23,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:01'),(12718249,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,23,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:01'),(12718250,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,23,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:01'),(8223483,2181564900,723966,3892314112,2576937,'Thunderman Ward 80',0,47,12,5725,6569,'Work with the Gatekeeper guild and whoever else will assist to recreate a permaward on a cache of the city.','2016-02-09 06:37:16'),(8832944,3959949796,3070,1744830464,39,'Bladestone',0,34,16,12049,-21247,'A rocky substance - hard and ridgid. Tons of dents and small knicks filter through this heavy rock. It appears to have been used in the olden days, for weaponry.','2016-04-27 02:40:18'),(8552594,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 1 MS 1',0,41,19,-3524,535,'This document represents the beliefs of the group currently seeking to reopen the Gathering of the Entranced.\r\nMISSION STATEMENT Part 1\r\nWe believe that the Nightmares of the City are Unawakened Dreamers whose connection to the DreamState is corrupted. We believe that by Cleansing them we repair their connection, improving their experience of the Dream and allowing them an increased chance to Awaken.','2016-03-22 21:00:43'),(8495875,2114456036,3070,738197504,42,'The Way- Hierarchy',0,34,16,11324,-21453,'Leader- His Holiness the Hootenancer : Jones: Mistress at Arms - Lady of  Lasso: Arlyana: 1st Disciple - Lad of Lariat :Uthanatos: 2nd Disciple - Chaplain of Chaps: Aileron: 3rd Disciple: Brother of Bandana: Restel. * All formal meetings shall be held in the Sepulchre of the Spur* ( Dueling Arena) ','2016-03-15 21:41:22'),(8408546,3876063716,330750,4160749568,2562087,'Kailee - FS 60',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'In line with your teachings, I\'d like for you to consider the nature of Lucidity -- not FateSendering, and not fire. What is it to be *Lucid* in your dreaming? Discuss this with at least two other dreamers whose opinions you respect. Then host a class and discussion on the nature of Lucidity with your fellow Dreamers. These don\'t need to be FateSenders, but it would preferable. Come up with creative means of ensuring participation in your class. Ensure a thorough report. ','2016-03-04 06:04:27'),(8552629,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 2 MS 2',0,41,19,-3545,518,'MISSION STATEMENT Part 2\r\nWe believe that promoting peace throughout the City will make it a place where the Newly Awakened will want to return to. By increasing the numbers of Newly Awakened who come to our City, and choose to return, our City will thrive.','2016-03-22 21:18:03'),(12717658,1644300480,791611393,10,0,'Fire Cyan Shield',0,8,17,28637,-7066,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(8495878,2114456036,3070,738197504,42,'The Way- Tenets',0,34,16,11313,-21307,'ALL dreamers shall be treated respectfully. NO derogatory terms shall be used when speaking of women. HELP those in need. DEFEND the defenseless.  MOTTO: when faced with dishonor, confrontation or deceit, may the lasso turn your other cheek!!','2016-03-15 21:44:52'),(8515271,856164836,3070,738197504,42,'Insignia Pin',0,34,16,11281,-21420,'A shining golden pin in the shape of a Lasso','2016-03-18 05:00:20'),(12717657,218368072,66332,10775,0,'Tan Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9142981,403180008,2866,2063597568,39,'Leave these be!',0,18,17,8173,-13385,'These power tokens are of the utmost importance.  Taking these will result in me murdering you.  I will have your guts as garters and I will be wearing your corpses\' face... as underwear.','2016-06-05 04:21:08'),(12717656,1107429568,555812865,10,0,'Fire Jade Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717655,285345984,218957825,5,0,'Blood Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(8552663,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 4 Ess',0,41,19,-3524,503,'ESSENCES\r\nEssences are a connection to the person whom they came from. Nightmare Essences are a connection to the Unawakened who experiences the Dream as a Nightmare. Through careful manipulation we can use this connection to effect them within the Dream.\r\nAll the Major Essence arts (Cleanse, Banish, and Imprison Nightmare) were designed by ancient SoulMasters to use Nightmare Essences to aid the Unawakened.','2016-03-22 21:23:44'),(8552662,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 3 Prob',0,41,19,-3496,512,'PROBLEM\r\nLike us, the Unawakened experience the DreamState, but unconsciously and don\'t feel the call to the City, their dreams are generally spent in the Chaos. When they wander into the City the sudden stress of Order can cause them to instinctively form a crude avatar, a Nightmare. Once they have formed an avatar in the City they are called back to the City, experiencing the Dream as a Nightmare.','2016-03-22 21:21:40'),(8552664,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 5 Sol 1',0,41,19,-3469,492,'SOLUTIONS Part 1\r\nCleanse Nightmare uses harmonic energy to purify the Unawakened\'s connection to the DreamState and bolstering them against future corruptions. This frees them from experiencing the Dream as Nightmares without otherwise restricting their access to the Dream, allowing them an increased chance to Awaken.','2016-03-22 21:26:37'),(8552697,1678248420,3070,2650800128,41,'GoE Beliefs 6 Sol 2',0,41,19,-3506,487,'SOLUTIONS Part 2\r\nBanish Nightmare forces the Nightmares from the City to the Chaos where they can\'t form an avatar and Imprison Nightmares binds the Nightmares to our courtyard not allowing them to wander the City in Nightmare form.\r\nDrain Essence doesn\'t affect the Nightmares directly, it simply absorbs the strength of the Essence creating only a temporary bound with the Unawakened.','2016-03-22 21:29:12'),(10164530,3876063716,2690046,4160749568,2699559,'Avayla - Deafen 10',0,47,5,-2928,3857,'Search throughout the City for rooms that seem to have loud, even deafen, noises in them by their own nature. Find at least three of these for me. Having found them, be prepared to discuss the nature of noise in the City. ','2016-10-08 21:34:06'),(8657746,688392676,3070,2734686208,42,'Flame ruin ',0,41,5,-86,-6764,'the art of flame ruin was created by an ancient dreamsmith called Balthus he was trying to make a small spark to light his pipe, he instead created a raginf ball of fire which is what we know today as flame ruin he burnt off what little hair he had creating this art and suffered much ridicule due to his hair loss he was able to get the last laugh he was rumored to have burnt the hair of 5 dreamsmiths off before running off laughing madly to use this art you must stand still untill it is completely evoked ','2016-04-05 01:38:21'),(8658258,1292372452,6097918,2046820352,2576938,'TMan Reflect70',0,47,12,5725,6570,'Reflecting back to your old City, spout off several things that were different in your time, that you wish you still had in this City.  Find something obtainable and recreate this for this city. Use as many dreamers as you can for help. Make this a nice sized project for either your house, or the city as a whole.','2016-04-05 03:28:56'),(12717654,302123200,286328833,10,0,'Fire Blood Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717653,33687744,185272321,10,0,'Fire Chalk Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9074129,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'The Forging Circle',0,43,5,-11016,1621,'Pazin Nalis\r\n*Apprentices-Vampyro, Xyn Rhade, Em\'et\r\nJaysen Grey-Forge Master Dreamersmith of the circle\r\nPrayenth and Aethimir- Arts development\r\n\r\nNames that may or may not be related-Cynthaya, Amaranthine, Sethyn, Ethan','2016-05-27 23:04:33'),(9004746,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ The Cell~ ',0,41,11,-6945,-2240,'the cell is cold and dark, how many days has it been? time and space no longer exist. How did I get here, my vision os shrouded, I can\'t remember. The voices echo through the dark. I dig at the walls until my fingers bleed. I call out to no one, my cries and protests lost in the void. No light at the end of the tunnel. I sleep, wrapped in a blanket of misery, disdain and resignation.... ~c~','2016-05-19 05:09:52'),(8655206,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: T4',0,41,19,-3820,517,'\r\nThe fourth tennet of the Preserver Conclave is the Duty to Act.\r\n\r\nOur membership shall have no excuse for failure to Act in the service of Underlight. All members are expected, and indeed, required to Act in the service of Underlight. Indecision and inaction are the primary causes of stagnation, or a failure to Grow. \r\n\r\nAll membership, from the highest ranks to the lowest, shall be required to remember the Duty to Act in the service of Underlight, at all times. ','2016-04-04 17:05:02'),(8657711,2936539620,3070,2734686208,42,'Soul evoke ',0,41,5,521,-6329,'Soul evoke is a very powerful and dangerous art it cost the user 1 permanent dreamsoul to evoke. it was created somewhere around the time of the dreamstrike masters to prevent one from being dreamstruck as you could cast soul evoke if collapsed and restore yourself or perhaps collapse the dreamstriker before they could strike someone from the dream. you can\'t use items of any kind while as a soulsphere only the will, lucid, resilience, insight you have when collapsed. it has its purpose as an art, at cost.','2016-04-05 01:26:51'),(8655525,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Palisades',0,41,19,-3829,500,'\r\nThe Preserver Conclave assumes resonsibility for maintaining and protecting the Palisades. As an institution capable of denying Dreamer\'s Freedom, the Palisades are a danger, but a necessity. They shall serve as a means of solving those problems which cannot otherwise be killed. Wraiths, they have been called. \r\n\r\nDreamers of Underlight should never be imprisoned within. It is not a place for Dreamers. Great care should be taken whenver entering the Palisades, let alone attempting to work within.','2016-04-04 18:08:58'),(8655491,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Law (1/2)',0,41,19,-3788,471,'\r\nLaws shall be debated and decided upon the formation of the Preserver Conclave. All founding members shall have an equal say, regardless of future or present rank. When the laws are thusly written, they shall be recorded in the Library of the Conclave for all membership to know and remember. \r\n\r\nAfter the initial formation of the Conclave, membership shall meet once a month, on a meeting date agreed upon by both Superiors, to propose new laws, or amendements to former laws. ','2016-04-04 17:55:30'),(8655300,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Branches',0,41,19,-3845,499,'\r\nThe Preserver Conclave shall be split into two branches: The Conclave Knights, and the Conservators. Each branch will be led by one Superior, and one Sentinel. \r\n\r\nThe purpose of the two branches will be to divide responsibility for service of Underlight, and to maintain the integrity of the Preserver Conclave throughout time. \r\n','2016-04-04 17:19:48'),(8655078,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: T2',0,41,19,-3789,485,'\r\nThe second tennet of the Preserver Conclave is Growth.\r\n\r\nTo Grow allows one opportunity to serve Underlight more fully. Dreaming without Growth is futility. Failing to Grow is a failure to serve Underlight, which is core to the Preserver Conclave.\r\n\r\nGrowth is not limited to Sphere, and Arts; one can Grow in many ways. The Preservers seek to Grow in all ways. No path may be rejected without first Understanding. ','2016-04-04 16:35:47'),(8655110,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Preserver Conclave',0,41,19,-3823,480,'The Preserver Conclave shall serve all Dreamers, from the edge of the Edgeward Barrows. The Preservers shall recognize Need in the Dream, for: | Understanding | Growth | Freedom | Duty to Act |\r\n\r\nThese four tennets will govern the actions of the Preserver Conclave for all Dreams, for all time. They may be expanded upon, but these are our core. ','2016-04-04 16:38:05'),(8655524,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Essences',0,41,19,-3858,520,'\r\nThe Preserver Conclave believes Nightmares to be unawakened dreamers touching briefly with Underlight, and their essences should thusly be treated with care. This said, all methods can serve: \r\n| Banishing allows the unawakened mind escape, and thus peace. \r\n| Imprisonment stores the chaos, separating it from the mind of the unawakened.\r\n| Cleansing transmutes the chaos within, releasing the mind from its influence.\r\n\r\nDraining does not help the unawakened mind, but does not harm it either. ','2016-04-04 18:04:53'),(8655142,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: T1',0,41,19,-3775,460,'\r\nThe first tennet of the Preserver Conclave is Understanding. \r\n\r\nTo serve the City Underlight, and all its Dreamers, we strive to Understand all things; even that which we may disagree with. Especially that which we may find distasteful. Understanding leads to opportunity. Opportunity to expand upon that which serves Underlight, and opprtunity to destroy that which harms it.\r\n\r\nWe know and accept that Understanding can never be truly complete. We do our Duty as the Conclave permits. ','2016-04-04 16:47:30'),(8655174,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: T3',0,41,19,-3807,502,'\r\nThe third tennet of the Preserver Conclave is Freedom. \r\n\r\nAll Dreamers deserve Freedom. No one should fear being true to oneself. Indeed, being true to oneself is one\'s Duty. With this recognized, Dreamers must also Understand that all choices have consequences. Being faced with those consequences is not a denial of Freedom; it is the cost of it.\r\n\r\nNo Dreamer should be denied his/her Freedom of choice. This is a sacred right which the Preserver Conclave will fight, whenever necessary, to protect. \r\n','2016-04-04 16:55:37'),(8655364,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave Knights',0,41,19,-3827,493,'\r\nThe Conclave Knights shall be responsible for making known the Will of the Conclave outside of the house. To serve Underlight in combat, and in force. They will serve as the primary defenders and warriors of the Preserver Conclave. \r\n\r\nTheir duties are not exclusive to combat, however. They shall be responsible for representing the house in foreign affairs. They must, above all else, remember the Duty to Act. ','2016-04-04 17:34:32'),(8655492,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Law (2/2)',0,41,19,-3811,489,'\r\nFor the week following proposed amendments or new law, there shall be a voting process by the house. Superiors shall collect and record votes. A majorty, 2/3rds vote is required to add or amend a law. ','2016-04-04 17:58:00'),(8655428,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'Conclave: Ranking',0,41,19,-3845,500,'\r\nLeadership of the Preserver Conclave shall be identified as detailed below: \r\n\r\nRulers are known as Superiors, for they hold dominion over their branch of the Conclave. \r\n\r\nGuardians are known as Sentinels, and they shall serve as the right hand of the Superior of their branch. \r\n\r\nAt all times there must be two Superiors, and two Sentinels. One for each branch of the Preserver Conclave. ','2016-04-04 17:48:56'),(8655427,3775400420,3070,3103784960,42,'The Conservators',0,41,19,-3835,526,'\r\nThe Conservator branch shall be responsible for the inner mechanisms of the Preserver Conclave. Maintaining the house stores, vaults, library. They are responsible for the laws and rules that govern the Conclave, and keeping careful watch for violation of those laws within the Conclave. \r\n\r\nConservators shall be responsible for gathering knowledge for the dual purposes of both Growth and Understanding. They shall further these tennets within the membership of the Conclave whenever possible. ','2016-04-04 17:44:57'),(8657781,2483554788,3070,2734686208,42,'Paralyze',0,41,5,525,-6413,'a good friend of renrut nek named t\'kaa was a kind of a healer he studied soulmaster arts to nearly rival his own focus arts, he made it his job to care for those with debilitating afflictions like paraplegics , people who suffered with arthritis and other diseases of the bone he wanted to know how a dreamers avatar could be plagued with such ailments he came to find out that sometimes a perfectly healthy person in there shard would be stricken with ailments in the dream and vise versa. he began working ','2016-04-05 01:45:02'),(8657783,2483554788,3070,2734686208,42,'Paralyze 2',0,41,5,527,-6428,'on an art and got 3 of his friends to help him out. the first of them he cast the art on began talking non stop for 2 seconds of jibberish. he tweeked a bit then the second person he cast it on fell striaght to the floor with no sense of balance. with a bit more work he quickly cast the art on his 3rd friend before he could run off and he stoped dead in his tracks un able to move. and now we have the art of paralyze !','2016-04-05 01:48:07'),(12717621,1543768072,83952433,10752,0,'Beige Teal Charm',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717620,553781440,370542593,6,0,'Blood Fire Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717619,268568768,269486081,4,0,'Chalk Blood Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(9713301,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,21,30,11542,-12594,'Darkness is both friend and enemy.','2016-08-14 03:46:19'),(8755959,822610404,3070,570425344,39,'Tribunal of Solara2',0,41,9,2684,-9385,'Honor, Courage, and Justice. It remained their never-ending duty to serve as the Protectors of the City of Dreams, against the wickedness of dreamers and beasts alike. Their tenets were: Honor, Valor, Justice and Humility. The honorable House of Tribunals worked to remain mindful not to cross into the path of tyranny, or to be labeled among the ranks of warmongers. They avoided conflict wherever possible (though there was trouble with House Orgoth). They sought to defend, never to be on the offensive.','2016-04-17 08:44:43'),(9133623,788598009,386401290,0,0,'Lucidity Stone',0,17,25,235,-11982,'A large grey stone, rippling with lucidic energy.','2016-06-04 03:34:20'),(12717618,1342245000,168100882,0,0,'Chalk Teal Alteror',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(8720799,1124600292,3070,2315255808,39,'Em\'',0,47,10,-5332,6375,'Em\', I\'m here. Lookin\' for you. I hear you\'ve been fiddlin\' with things you shouldn\'t, at least without me. I miss you. I\'m not late, I\'m right on time. Find me soon. - Your Partner','2016-04-12 23:19:41'),(8728033,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Sphere Requirements',0,47,10,-4353,5058,'\r\n~Em\'et\'s Sphere Requirements:\r\nAll major arts learned.\r\n~3rd sphere and beyond:\r\nFocus art to Sphere.\r\nA number of focus arts equal to the Sphere sought (major or minor) arts to Sphere. Three for 3rd sphere, Four for 4th sphere, etc, etc. ','2016-04-13 17:41:29'),(8754180,855640437,13437953,0,0,'Debris',0,18,9,8486,-1581,'A large bright yellow chunk of jagged rock.','2016-04-17 02:40:12'),(9889085,151521764,3070,1023410176,43,'AoE Beliefs 1',0,22,30,10042,-10508,'The Alliance of the Eclipse is an OpenSoul, Enlightened House.\r\nWe are a house of study dedicated to better understanding the Dream. We seek to shape a brighter, safer future for the City through innovation and ingenuity.\r\nIndividual dreamers experience the Dream in different ways and through different methods, thus each connection to the City is different. A person may have a weaker or stronger connection to the city at any given time, and thus the effects the city has on an individual may vary.','2016-09-04 16:02:05'),(8745959,2668104164,6360062,2550136832,2575911,'SenseD30-Krodoc',0,47,12,5901,5496,'How much do you rely on your senses? Have a few trusted dreamers be your senses for you- all five.  Close your eyes and have them walk you somewhere. Have them touch items and explain in full detail what they are, so you can guess what they are.  I would like to discuss the lesson once you have completed this and reported to me. Remember to go through all five senses.','2016-04-16 05:00:18'),(8755960,822610404,3070,570425344,39,'Tribunal of Solara3',0,41,9,2676,-9380,'However, they intended to seek out where only injustice thrived, and bring order to where chaos reigned. Justice and order were paramount in their goals. They believed the \"shards\" aka mares were to be disposed of, and any that offered any kind of aid to the vile beasts would be be eradicated with prejudice.','2016-04-17 08:45:54'),(12717617,1342245000,151323662,0,0,'Chalk Teal Alteror',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(8755958,822610404,3070,570425344,39,'Tribunal of Solara1',0,41,9,2684,-9385,'In the second variant shift of Idoaclecia, we landed in a City very different than what we were used to. The houses that used to be open were either closed or taken over by a new faction, and a woman was seeking a following to open the Valley. This woman was known as the Woman in White - or to her followers, the Grand Council. This house was The Tribunal of Solara.\r\n\r\nThe Tribunal of Solara stood together under one banner, each committing to eternally undertake and ever uphold the vows of:','2016-04-17 08:42:56'),(8768275,101190120,2896,3523215360,40,'Sphere',0,47,6,-3509,5862,'Prepare ten sample sphere tasks for Akkadian\'s perusal. One for each sphere you are able to write based on your sphere, and any others above third sphere to equal ten total.','2016-04-19 01:35:14'),(8784363,1091045860,3070,1627389952,41,'Portrait',0,17,30,12118,-8695,'A beautiful sketch done in colored chalk pastels. It depicts the facade of Calenture in rich reds, standing forefront is Aileron drawn expertly down to every handsome detail. Above his head are a circlet of emerald trail gems which spin and shine brilliantly - depicting a Soulmaster Halo. Written in elegant script along the bottom are the words. ~You are on the right path~ a small ~c~ is in the lower left corner.','2016-04-20 20:13:30'),(8879794,268021,1393889025,14222082,0,'Extraction Device',0,17,25,-710,-12440,'A small strange silver rod.  At the top of the rod is a bright red button.','2016-05-03 03:00:42'),(9004748,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ Wonderland~',0,41,11,-6901,-2181,'Exquisite purity wafts from the sky. Trees glistening like diamonds, sparkle in the moonlight. An awed reverie as you walk in cotton silence, clearing your mind of the day.  Your breath in the air gracefully floats then disappears into the night.\r\n','2016-05-19 05:14:30'),(9075438,2265450980,3070,4261412864,41,'Calenture: Purpose',0,47,2,-2910,-623,'House Calenture is a self contained warrior based house that holds as its purpose two main objectives, both of equal importance. To Defend the City of Underlight from hostile forces, and to Banish the Nightmares from the city.','2016-05-28 03:38:54'),(8935992,2131233252,3070,2281701376,42,'Beadwork Mat',0,47,13,-8091,-392,'This beadwork mat is roughly three hands across and depicts the eclipse of the sable moon in relief.  The detailed working of the beads leaves the outline of the moon in bright silver against a shaded night background, the reverse side, shows the raised eclipse in chalk and abyss over a berry background.','2016-05-10 03:11:28'),(10172772,1711802856,2862,1627389952,41,'Cia\'s entry  Horror',0,41,8,608,-8880,'Book cover and prologue for the new contest. Horror Genre.                  *c','2016-10-09 23:37:37'),(9499753,526820,3070,335544320,39,'Zsa\'s Thingamajica',0,47,13,-8100,-772,'A  reed that measures 3 feet in length. Along the long swirled reed is carvings of ancient warriors and sigil symbols of foci elemens. The projectile  is activated by insight is venonmous in nature.\r\n','2016-07-19 00:15:23'),(8941692,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,4,4821,-4467,'The Dreamsmith Kelrith made a grave mistake when trying to call a new artifact into the dream.','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941704,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,9,3962,-10277,'Shields absorb a percentage of the damage you suffer from an attack.','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941693,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,3,-2487,-5836,'Only those who have the Dreamsmith Mark can teach the power of Forge Talisman.','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941723,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,7,4009,-6752,'There are two basic mares you, as a new dreamer, will encounter: an Emphant and a Bogrom.','2016-05-10 16:59:59'),(8941686,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,3,-2548,-5832,'A question most often asked: do our actions in the dream affect the waking world?','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941670,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,3,-2615,-5831,'There are two basic mares you, as a new dreamer, will encounter: an Emphant and a Bogrom.','2016-05-10 16:41:17'),(8941699,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,4,4821,-3929,'Dream wisdom: if you find yourself in a rift with a Dark Mare and you do not wish to be collapsed... leave the rift.','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941744,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,9,4032,-10276,'The second color of an alteror determines its function. Blood brings Vision, fire brings Resist Fear, gold brings Protection, jade brings Free Action and teal brings Chamele.','2016-05-10 16:59:59'),(8941731,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,6,-3526,-7851,'Your blade is your most elementary weapon. As with all weapons, it is never to be used against other Dreamers except in self-defence','2016-05-10 16:59:59'),(8941709,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,4,4818,-4834,'Efforts yield reward, not words alone.','2016-05-10 16:50:38'),(8941787,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,7,4006,-6752,'Guardians gain power when they initiate new dreamers into their house, but they lose even more if an initiate leaves the House.','2016-05-10 17:08:29'),(8941796,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,41,6,-3526,-7844,'Ghea was the first dreamer to collapse Tehthu after the foul Dark Mare entered the dream.','2016-05-10 17:08:29'),(12717616,1409550344,83952412,10752,0,'Jade Teal Charm',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(9004844,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~You Don\'t Know~',0,41,11,-6911,-2193,'Anguish, bitterness, anger..pushed aside. trying to decide when to forgive, or if. You don\'t know how I feel. Moments of indecision, cowardice, swept under the carpet. It makes you all feel better to forget, pretend it never happened. You don\'t know how I feel. Hours, days, months, replay in my mind, an infinite trail of nothing and no one. You don\'t care how I feel, you never did. Masters of Sparkle and Shine. Theatrical Masks..Priorities...  ~c~','2016-05-19 05:28:37'),(9589807,2131233256,5376815,2365587456,2624039,'Vampyric Draw - 10',0,41,19,-3424,232,'\"They drew first blood\".  We need to know the weaknesses of our enemies.  Discover what they may be of the three houses that stand against our faith.  In what manner may we exploit that weakness?  Be very detailed for the success of your efforts may lead to swift house action.  ~D','2016-07-30 04:12:40'),(9629853,1913129448,5507923,1493172224,2561835,'Dina\'s Vapors',0,47,9,-4735,3472,'I hear this art used to be different than what it once was. How is it different? Was it changed for the better? What does it do and how does it do it? Learn as many specifics as you can.','2016-08-04 01:37:24'),(8990711,940050920,2427702,2063597568,2566951,'Dreamblade 60',0,47,11,5926,4156,'I want you to use the University to teach of the various levels of Dreamblade.  Specifically I want you to explain the physical differences between each plateau between 0 and 60, and why they are more durable and what makes them last longer.  I want you to obtain samples, if possible, of the 6 different levels for inspection and comparison. I would like 2 nights to discuss the blade and its importance in the dream city, both as a symbol and a weapon.','2016-05-17 04:42:47'),(9004713,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ The Puppet~',0,41,11,-6916,-2208,'The puppet danced happily, pblivious to all else except the hands that controlled the strings...but the strings became tangled and twisted beyond reparation, and so they were cut...one...by one...by one.. and the puppet fell int oa useless heap of despair.  ~c~','2016-05-19 05:06:58'),(9004747,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~Lament~',0,41,11,-6924,-2223,'I wonder if you know, tha tI look for you each dream..That I long to hear your voice. that when you speak I hang on every word. Your smile and wit enthralls me, when you stand near me, my heart beats faster. when you are gone, I despair. I have waited for years..I wonder of you feel the same..I\'ll keep on wondering, I\'m a coward, I lament... ~c~','2016-05-19 05:12:35'),(9004780,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~Kings & Queens~',0,41,11,-6893,-2149,'In and out of glowing portals dreamers come and go. Apathy takes hold of those destined for greatness, the quiet ones. they did not hear their calling.  Avarice and greed overcome those who have achieved such greatness..Kings and Queens of Art and Might..Secretly feared and loathed by all...Intimidated by none.  ~c~','2016-05-19 05:18:42'),(12717615,553781440,303171585,9,0,'Blood Fire Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(9004812,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~Disappear~',0,41,11,-6887,-2171,'I want to disappear... confusion, pain, no hope,  I am going mad..angry, bitter, an empty soul and emptier heart craves to be whole, needed, wanted, useful. So distraught and full of despair, there are no words to describe this.  ~c~','2016-05-19 05:24:35'),(10342572,688392680,1706811,4194304000,2561833,'Reweave ~ mini',0,47,9,-4890,3540,'Call me a glutton for punishment, but I am intrigued that you want to open a house.  Give me the run down of the beliefs,how you would gather support and open it.','2016-10-31 04:05:53'),(9785438,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'First Tenant',0,21,30,11550,-12355,'\"The only limitations that exist are those which we place upon ourselves\" : Many fail to achieve their goals and potential due to self-imposed limitations. But why? Limitations are meant to be faced and conquered so that the achievement of our full potential can be attained. This is the aim of the Peace Corpse. To work, together, to conquer obstacles, illusions, and fear so that *all* achieve, and then surpass, their full potential and dreams.','2016-08-22 21:34:13'),(12717652,218368072,66327,10805,0,'Tan Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9075596,2265450980,3070,4261412864,41,'Calenture: OpenSoul',0,47,2,-2896,-611,'As an open soul house, we do not concern ourselves on an overall level with questions of the Soul or Illumination.  Our members are welcome to believe as their personal beliefs direct them.','2016-05-28 04:17:43'),(12717651,1812006856,604242446,0,0,'Beige Cyan Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9059561,3976727012,3070,2751463424,42,'Ornate Box',0,22,30,9158,-11298,'An intricate wooden box with the Dual Triune on each half of the top.  opened down the middle and closed tight with a shiny brass latch.  Opened inside you see an array of brushes made of the finest hairs and wooden handles with various animals painted on them, on one side and colors on the other.  Looking at the colors you see each one swirls and shifts in the light.  Slight energy sparks emit off the colored liquids as if they have been infused with elemental foci.\r\n','2016-05-25 23:22:52'),(9048871,252185064,4983572,1224736768,2566952,'Mini - Show 50',0,47,11,6271,4367,'Showing those you consider foe\'s respect often leads to respect being returned to you, an important thing to have as a leader.  I want you to (begrudgingly, if necessary) show interest in two dreamers you can\'t normally stomach.  Find out something about them that you didn\'t know through direct coversation. \r\n','2016-05-24 17:31:26'),(12719373,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(9067460,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~Wax & Wane~',0,41,11,-6936,-2230,'My heart waxes and wanes like an ocean tide. It always has. I try so hard not to let it be so, but in the end I am a soul endlessly searching for things to fill an emptiness that I cannot describe or explain. It has always been there and it seems it will always be. I envy those who find what makes them feel whole, as I continue to tread water in an endless ocean of despair. \r\n','2016-05-27 00:53:26'),(9067046,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'Old to New',0,41,11,-6877,-2134,'The old dream is gone, with it many friends, foes, hopes, plans and desires. Holding on to ancient ideals is futile, old dreams die...to be born anew, as the Phoenix from the ashes. ','2016-05-26 23:50:22'),(12717650,385943688,604046351,0,0,'Night Blood Alteror',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717649,2516649928,755106319,0,0,'Cyan Plum Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717648,151259208,66346,10808,0,'Plum Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9074192,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Idoaclesian Chaks ',0,43,5,-10952,1595,'Chakram ranges are after the change. Before this they were higher damage ranges.\r\n2nd Sphere     3rd Sphere\r\n21-10 dam      31- 9-16 damage\r\n22- 5-15           32- 5-21\r\n23- 6-15           33- 2-24\r\n24- 7-14           34- 9-18\r\n25- 1-20           35- 3-24\r\n26- 3-18           36- 7-22\r\n27- 2-20           37- 10-20\r\n28- 6-18           38- 15\r\n29- 8-16           39- 5-25\r\n30- 7-18   Effects- Azure/deaf,Leaf/poison,Beige/blind,plum/scare, sand/curseORpoison,Earth/stagORpara,Blood/breakcovenant, Silver/enfeeble','2016-05-27 23:20:17'),(9133622,788598009,856228872,0,0,'Lucidity Stone',0,43,10,3510,-7402,'A large grey stone, rippling with lucidic energy.','2016-06-04 03:33:54'),(10458040,134744552,4197189,2063597568,2751015,'Invis 60',0,47,11,5327,4417,'Once Invis becomes a higher level, dreamers tend to place more importance on Invis rather than Chamele. As a guild member, how do we encourage emphasis on both arts equally?  If you could change one thing about each art, what would it be?  Furthermore, is this the consensus of others? Ask a few other guild members their opinions.\r\n','2016-11-14 04:57:23'),(9949961,554174948,3070,251658240,43,'Vortex of Sorrow',0,47,13,-6501,67,'In your hands you hold an odd; something. It lacks a physical appearance aside from seeing odd colored strands of light that appear, here and there, as though swirling around an invisible center. As you look closer, you feel the strands weaving around you, and drawing in all of those feelings you wish were gone: anger, hatred, sorrow, fear, loss, guilt, grief...and more. You can sense them drawn down deep into the vortex and held there; their absence leaving a feeling of refreshement in their place.','2016-09-12 04:16:31'),(9117564,705169892,3070,3942645760,42,'Boots',0,41,3,-3469,-5156,'you see a pair of boots, made with the hardened skin of a Horron for the upper part, lined with the under belly of an Emphant for comfort. the soles made from a Shammy chest for durability. the laces are made fron an Emphant spine tendon for strenth, they dont smell good but will last a long time','2016-06-01 22:01:53'),(9166161,4043835876,3070,2751463424,42,'Trap',0,41,11,-5718,-2270,'A backdrop of blood and abyss seem to almost meld together.  A home is off in the distance on fire near the horizon line. Next to the home almost transparent is a feminine figure. Closer up, a child on it\'s stomach, hands outstretched infront of him, fingers stained with dirt. Near the child\'s left is a forest of deep greens and blacks. The bottom of the painting is painted to look like scorch marks as if a flame licked it.  The paintng rests in a frame, hinged on the right side.  Another painting attached','2016-06-08 00:09:19'),(12717647,3540060104,939590157,0,0,'Gold Tan Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717646,201394120,3976462865,0,0,'Beige Chalk Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717645,687933384,251855377,0,0,'Plum Fire Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9133624,788598009,386663434,0,0,'Lucidity Stone',0,17,25,160,-11968,'A large grey stone, rippling with lucidic energy.','2016-06-04 03:34:42'),(9459532,4043835876,3070,2734686208,42,'Shortcuts Continued',0,22,30,10009,-10474,'#5 harrow to Albino East valley exit to east valley straight across is albino entrance from harrow or vise versa #6 Albino to Lost caves Umbric sewer hall to winneys wonderings to sanctuary to straight ahead to upper umbric turn right to lost caves #7 Lost caves to gloom peaks Middle basin exit follow creek around go straight thru room with boggy follow creek around to gloom peaks entrance #8 gloom peaks to Cairn or sorrow. exit gloom thru cliff face pass thru first cave turn left first on right to cairn ','2016-07-14 02:54:43'),(9166195,3406301668,3070,2751463424,42,'Trapping',0,41,11,-5725,-2255,'A urban backdrop is painted in the background. Small dots that get bigger as the eye gets closer to the foreground turning into figures of people.  At the bottom center of the picture is a long wooden table, scrolls, weapons of all likes, and coins strewn about. Four figures sit at the table, their faces obscured except for the eyes that look to their right. A man, sitting in on his own, long brown hair,blood eyes and a smirk. He holds in one arm a body, bleeding from the neck while in it\'s back a knife.','2016-06-08 00:16:14'),(9932301,526820,3070,637534208,43,'The Hotai Plague 2',0,41,10,-2301,-9545,'individual. He knew his sciences under of all that, he began spending time at the Emergence Academy. Most dreamers didn\'t think much of his experimentation until suddenly dreamers began becoming ill. Their skin would blacken, ooze would drip from their eyes and mouths','2016-09-10 01:44:48'),(9166198,4060613092,3070,2751463424,42,'Trapped',0,41,11,-5739,-2239,'The whole painting is covered in flames from the top to the bottom. Inside the flames shadows seem to dance almost moving on their own. Each shadow has a trail of red that pools at the bottom of them.  Not too far off in the distance a man, holding his head, hands dug into his hair, eyes bloodshot and crazed. His body is contorted and his body is half leaning off the side of a cliff, mouth open as if he is screaming. \r\n At the bottom more shadows, each with symbols on them you cannot understand. ','2016-06-08 00:21:07'),(9713487,856164836,3070,0,0,'Codex of Learning',0,21,30,11527,-12558,'If this is only a dream, then how can you be sure you are dreaming?','2016-08-14 04:14:22'),(9180488,526824,9505597,419430400,2565671,'CW-50',0,47,9,-4685,4090,'Organize and conduct a game that revolves around collecting something. What is collected and how someone wins is up to you. Aim for at least 5 participants, not including you. ','2016-06-09 21:52:20'),(9558151,2130773945,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams II',0,2,31,10291,-10207,'A tattered codex page, the parchment showing signs of age. Written upon the page are runes which glow with a red light. At the top of the page are three holes, spaced evenly apart with iron rings set into them.','2016-07-26 02:11:24'),(9589628,2181564900,2100222,3892314112,2624041,'Anyasha Curse 60',0,41,19,-3424,232,'Complete a project to show the dream that the Keepers are not only \"evil\" but can be a benefit to the dream as well.  I will not be judging your project on it\'s success, but on your efforts to complete it.  Your efforts should be worthy of a 60 plateau.','2016-07-30 03:40:35'),(9216057,1074268644,9178110,2046820352,2566954,'LadySilver | SenseD',0,22,30,7458,-13110,'Work with others on adjusting this art to sense what you really want to know. Maybe you\'d like to sense Zaxun and his army. Maybe puppy dogs and kitty cats. Maybe you\'d just like to find some fresh cake!  Work hard with others and make sure this report is worthy of this plat. The art may not work in the end, but I\'d like to know EVERY detail of how you may get it to work, someday. Trials are very acceptable, even the failed ones. ','2016-06-14 00:47:47'),(9499976,526820,3070,3841982464,39,'a bow shaped bow',0,47,13,-8047,-768,'this is a womans hair bow shaped into a powerful bow that shoots endless arrows and can influence things greatly by way of arts as well','2016-07-19 01:05:50'),(9216742,2835876324,1575934,4026531840,2579752,'Recharge 70',0,18,31,16567,-6349,'I wish for you to recharge interest in your \"gossip column\". However, epand on its original concept and grow it in some way. I will leave those specifics up to you, naturally. Also, while you work on that, come up with a quick guide to improving Recharge through the plateaus. Make efforts worthy of plateau to 70. **A**','2016-06-14 03:05:22'),(12717644,654379144,637993997,0,0,'Night Fire Alteror',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717643,1493239752,4009951762,0,0,'Plum Teal Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(9589872,4060153785,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams III',0,2,31,10268,-10211,'A page torn from the Codex of Immortal Dreams, cryptic runes are written across the page and glow with a golden light. Three holes were placed in the top of the page which have delicate iron rings placed within them.','2016-07-30 04:21:51'),(9508970,1074268644,4525054,2046820352,2564650,'Jade | FShaft 60',0,47,12,5057,6322,'We\'ve all seen dreamers create their own blades. Hold a class that shows others, in group fashion, how to create THEIR own. Have at least two successful blades created from this class or session. Test their knowledge and make sure they pass your test. I would like to see the blades upon completion.','2016-07-20 01:18:04'),(9314289,526820,3070,570425344,39,'Maren A\'s',0,41,4,3159,-5217,'Again = Po | Air = Vellak | All = Buur | Allow = Lax | Alteror = Dipi | Amulet = Bacca | And = En or Ulp | Anger = Grrth | Antidote = \'Dote | Any = Prak | AoE = Resancae | Art = Maxtrik | Artifact = Hruril | As = Aw | At = Ek | Ekattack = Pantz | Attacks = Attakjsks | Avatar = Aviktra | Avoid = Gwelf | Away = Vorasha','2016-06-26 01:01:04'),(9822791,856164836,3070,1191182336,40,'Order of Light (2)',0,47,2,-3914,518,'of the dreamers that came over from the Order believes that imprisoning is an efficient way of harvesting strength from essences. The art of banish, cleanse, and most importantly drain essence are not to be used by our members at the house without extreme scrutiny from the Circle of Rulers and then only on approved artifacts, and drain essence should -never- be evoked by any of our members and will be punished by immediate expulsion from the house. Whatever reason a member chooses to join, we all respect','2016-08-27 21:06:00'),(9329306,526824,5311304,4261412864,2565671,'Quest: WishBringer',0,47,9,-4709,4085,'Hypnotic - Therapist.  It is time - to convince rooms full of dreamers they are chickens, or monkeys or well anything.  Instead of using Hypnotic Weave to paralyze them.  Use your own hypnotic skills to get them to dance, sing, etc.  Mostly have fun figuring out creative ways to do it.  Group setting when possible and enjoy.\r\n','2016-06-28 01:47:52'),(9370360,940050916,3070,2063597568,39,'Political History',0,41,2,1143,-4276,'History is one of the most important aspects of the city.  Many teachers and scholars insist upon the teaching and research of histories, because of the importance it plays.  Many people who are part of those histories still dream.  Most love to rehash the \"glory days\" as well, take care or be drawn into a rant.  Those histories drive our present and are therefore inextricably linked to the future.  Research any history you can find. ','2016-07-03 03:21:34'),(9338518,2668104164,7343102,2550136832,2565671,'MiniDazzle-Blade',0,47,9,-5150,4080,'Dazzle me with your fake knowledge! Come up with new histories of all the houses, or random city folk.  Tell as many as you can about these histories and see if you can be believed. Make it good!','2016-06-29 02:09:39'),(10770034,3557296612,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | Learn',0,47,3,3790,1083,'Dreamers have proven themselves to turn on someone once houses don\'t benefit them. Our home is experiencing hardship currently. Sit in silently on some of our fellow housemates and gather a few opinions on their loyalties. Ensure a thorough report. Also, learn the mechanics of this art. ','2016-12-22 00:00:38'),(9459468,520620516,3070,2734686208,42,'Shortcuts',0,22,30,10009,-10512,'#1 To HC the cliff upper twisting road high road calenture way  #2 OoD-CoD ossuray entrance tomb of el-linar crossing paths the long curve southwest ring path hand of fate a quiet place ellies final choice ellies last descision CoD entrance #3 OoD-Chasm Higher Lambent exit Higherlambent flats to OoD #4 Threshcaves to Either rift Caves entrance Labrinth entraance 1st portal, 3rd portal 2nd portal all to the right temple of meditation up both stairs left side caudal right side dorsal ','2016-07-14 02:44:21'),(9411222,134744552,1510210,2063597568,2562087,'Forge 60',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'I want you to forge a new FateSender\'s guild.  Talk to those who are fatesenders (including BladeSlayer) and have them come to a consensus on what the guild is to be, and what your aspirations are.  Bring them all together under one roof and get a cohesive product.  Bring young fatesenders into the fold as well, make them part of the process.\r\n','2016-07-08 04:37:37'),(12576208,1711343560,335675921,0,0,'Cyan Elemen',0,6,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-07 17:43:58'),(10319697,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Mind Blank | Learn',0,33,22,294,22533,'There tends to be a great deal of useless information clouding our minds in the dream and circumventing our progress. Engage in some conversations with dreamers and identify some of these. Learn the basics of the art in addition to this. \r\n','2016-10-28 09:23:51'),(9370328,940050916,3070,2063597568,39,'Political Manual 1',0,41,2,1159,-4275,'The Dream City is rife with political complications.  There are several groups, groups within groups, splinter cells and usurpers.  There are three key elements that will help you operate in this city\'s political landscape.  1: Understanding History, 2: Understanding the houses, 3: Understanding popular opinion of the City.','2016-07-03 03:18:17'),(9370519,940050916,3070,2063597568,39,'Political Manual 5',0,41,2,1096,-4275,'It is important to remember that you\'re going to see a lot of anyone you see now. You have to forge a working relation with the majority of the dream city.  Whether or not you agree with their beliefs, their house, their house leaders or their practices... you\'re going to find yourself needing them at some point.  The final lesson: No-one can take your integrity away from you, you can only give it away.  Respect is earned and if you are not prepared to earn it, you will find yourself on the outside soon.','2016-07-03 03:50:26'),(9370456,940050916,3070,2063597568,39,'Popular Politics',0,41,2,1110,-4277,'Popular opinion drives much of the city. Though not a democracy in any way, popular opinion and contribution are key to an individual\'s success. Dreamers who become known for wearing out their welcome find doors shut and halos removed in their presence. 1 dreamer has little traction, but as soon as you have a following of 3 or 4, watch out.  On the other hand, if 98% of the dream are telling you something is a bad idea, know you are running the risk of ostracizing yourself.','2016-07-03 03:47:03'),(9370392,940050920,2869,2063597568,39,'House Politics',0,41,2,1127,-4277,'Ever want to get a room chatting about the old days?  Start talking about how one house beat up another.  The houses\' history is deep and entrenched in a bitter rivalry for top spot. Membership, battles, activities, accomplishments... these are all worn on each dreamer in the shape of the house crest they bear.  Knowing the key members of any house is crucial to know who you should and should not annoy.  Pushing a houses\' buttons is a great way to find yourself hunted down and collapsed.\r\n','2016-07-03 03:33:41'),(9718867,1325926884,3070,1744830464,39,'Vampiric Draw (I)b',0,41,5,190,-6352,'One such tactic was the creation of Vampiric Draw. As battles would rage, the spectre-like collection of Umbric Defenders would collect essences, and attack all foes - void of choosing a right versus wrong, or good versus evil mentality, while under a cloaked veil of sercrecy and seclusion. Vampiric Draw would be used to help speed up the conclusion of battles so the soulspheres could then be dispelled away from the plane until the Elder of Umbric (Nyjiman) would enter the City and serve as the buffer....','2016-08-14 21:11:27'),(9624664,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-8',0,41,10,-2555,-9420,'her lot... I said to the Shadow Lord, \"Please... I cannot take their bullying any longer... Make me powerful, I beg you..\" He told me he accepted me, and that I would be his General in his army.. I happily obliged.. As his shadow\'s entered my body.. I could no longer control myself, I seen my dreams, but it was as if I was simply dreaming with no control of my surroundings.. The last thing I could do was let out an epic howl that was heard throughout the entire city.. I rushed their facade....','2016-08-03 09:05:34'),(12719372,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10736928,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Return | Learn',0,47,3,3639,1215,'Energy always flows from a source to a sink. Remember that well. Everyone interacts differently in the dream based on their role and personality, but most people sort into one of two types with respect to their impact on other people: energy sources and energy sinks. Take two dreams to examine what dreamers in the dream are \"sinks\" and which are \"sources\". Your answers will be confedential. Your report will consist of warning me of these dreamers.  Also, learn the basics of the art. ','2016-12-18 06:30:37'),(9401562,526820,3070,1409286144,41,'LightHolders.',0,41,9,3020,-9496,'When I was first approached by the elder, He was shrouded in a very bright light that seemed to be an Aura flowing off of him, He showed me what I was destined for, I recevied multiple scrolls that could only be opened with the light, Once I was shown the way I trained dream after dream to perfect this Art. Once I could conjure the Light from within i was able to open the scrolls and it showed me the War that was going to begin between the Beasts and Dreamers. ','2016-07-07 02:51:46'),(9401565,526820,3070,1409286144,41,'LightHolders Pt.4',0,41,9,2975,-9496,'I feel as if the reason i have returned is the city is in need of the LightHolder talents that i hold the knowledge of. This time feels worse then ever, I am almost worried about the future of this city and its dreamers. LightHolders~Before we can reach the light we must first understand the darkness~','2016-07-07 02:59:25'),(9401564,526820,3070,1409286144,41,'LightHolders Pt.3 ',0,41,9,2990,-9499,'The darkness that all LightHolders were trained to fight no matter the cost, not even if it meant their own lives. The darkness brough a number of beasts strong and weak. The war started, As it waged dream after dream multiple casulties were taken on both sides. I do not remember much towards the end i just know we defeated the Darkness hoping it would never return to our city. After that war was over I was unable to dream and reach the city again, until a few nights ago. ','2016-07-07 02:57:03'),(10007911,671615460,3070,2281701376,40,'Reweave History 1',0,41,5,461,-6921,'Reweave was created by the DreamWright Mantic, who was also part of the Forger\'s Circle.  He was very concerned with searching for a way to strengthen the City walls, and creating new things.  Mantic searched for a new art that would help him strengthen the City walls.  His first attempt at creating that art was Reweave.  He found it too weak, even at high plateaus, to affect something as immense as walls, but it was good for spot repairs.  Taking his knowledge a bith further he decided to try.....','2016-09-19 09:25:51'),(9401563,526820,3070,1409286144,41,'LightHolders Pt. 2',0,41,9,3006,-9499,'It told me of a war that would start with a single blood drop falling from the sky. I was in the Edgeward House when The Wardens were there Ra\'as was the leader, Once it happened they started to believe what i was saying after that some dreamers prepared others were skeptical. Before the beasts came i devoted Training a small few that were introduced into the LightHolder clan, we trained dream after dream until they perfected the art, Not long after the Darkness came. ','2016-07-07 02:54:16'),(9418652,1141377508,3070,2734686208,42,'Restore Chart !',0,41,2,393,-3506,'Restore chart as per Arnaya\'s research and  Conformation unplatted 1-5 plat 10, 2-6, plat 20 3-10, plat 304-11, plat 40 5-12, plat 50 6-15  results tested from 40 minimum evokes for quality control purposes ! ','2016-07-09 04:12:39'),(10063521,2198342116,2100222,4261412864,2562345,'Curse 10 - Dreiko',0,41,23,-3114,2951,'Ah, cursing... so much stress relief and drama all rolled into one package.  I would like you to help relieve some of the stress on some of your members, by subtly giving their curses a tangible effect for a little bit.  Pick a couple of people that seem to need it the worst.  Let me know how they responded to their curses being manifest.  Be creative and try to have some fun with this.','2016-09-25 22:30:39'),(9483783,4026599929,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams 4',0,2,31,10234,-10212,'A worn codex page frayed along the edges.  A cipher of glowing white runes cover the page.  On the top of the page are three holes, each surrounded by a delicate iron circle.  ','2016-07-17 01:28:29'),(9748055,1913129448,1706823,1493172224,2586667,'Portal Weaving',0,43,5,-12803,-1073,'You seek to lock a portal, eh? This is no simple feat. A ward, while blocking passage, is temporary. You seek to do more than that. How would this be accomplished? Has this been done in the past? I think much research is in your future. Once ready gather up your theories and ideas, as well as others to help you and make your attempts. As many as you feel is necessary to accomplish your goal.','2016-08-18 07:26:55'),(10671225,4144499172,9178110,1392508928,2803495,'Sense Datoken 30',0,47,11,5690,4311,'This art is one of those that really doesn\'t need to be platted. But you are going to change that. Please think of what it should do as it progresses. Tell you what room the Datoken is in? What form they are? What arts they have on? Think of some ways that the art can progress that would be feasible. Get input from others if you want to. <T>','2016-12-10 06:51:12'),(9630524,788596665,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams VII',0,2,31,10260,-10229,'A worn codex page, a cipher of runes written across its page that seem burned into the surface rather than written. An aura surrounds the page, causing light to dim around it. Three holes at its top, bound with rusted iron rings.','2016-08-04 03:45:25'),(9582265,1074268644,5508094,2046820352,2624042,'HealAur10 |Anyasha ',0,41,19,-3424,232,'Pull bits of chaos from the sky and draw it up into a safe container.  Work with others to see how the smallest of bits of chaos can harm a dreamer. Find a way to heal them. Is Healing Aura the strongest art for such a thing? If it isn\'t, theorize on how to make it stronger, for I fear the end is coming upon us.','2016-07-29 03:20:44'),(9713756,4144499172,1248254,1392508928,2576935,'Chamele - 10',0,47,12,5699,6578,'Chamele is usefull at times. It\'s also anoying. Think of some good hidden places that have more potential than they are showing. Think of it as a game of \"hide and seek\" in the City. Pick your three favorite and tell me about them. <T>','2016-08-14 05:14:03'),(9541856,3993045369,117966079,0,0,'Grok\'s Keg of Ale',0,18,8,8423,2422,'A small wooden cask, about a foot in diameter.  A small spout in the front with a turnable knob.  The wooden cask is filled with the finest dwarven ale, never seeming to run low.','2016-07-24 04:41:39'),(9670021,4060153785,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams I',0,2,31,10281,-10210,'A piece of parchment, three holes at its top bound with iron rings. Unfamilar runes are inked into the page, faded but clear. A dark aura surrounds the page, giving off a greenish hue.','2016-08-09 00:49:25'),(12718890,100730824,218235409,0,0,'Cyan Chalk Elemen',0,39,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:17'),(9624566,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-4',0,41,10,-2553,-9474,'peers in spars... Of course they still won every now and then but hell who cares, i\'m top tier in technique by now so their spheres mean\'t nothing to me.. Eventually my competitive attitude and nature made nobody in the city want to train me.. I use to wonder why they never wanted to see me grow.... I never planned to turn on my city, I just wanted to be their champion... I loved them.. I just wanted them to love me and accept me for who I am.... ','2016-08-03 08:53:00'),(10385369,53381,13437953,0,0,'Tears',0,26,2,194,-3516,'','2016-11-05 04:58:12'),(10351079,1997015528,2860,1627389952,41,'Manly Trousers',0,21,16,-3070,-2875,'For a manly man, these trousers are made of heavy linen, resistant to chak fire, agoknight teeth marks and seepage or spillage of any kind. Dark blue, perfectly matching a stylish  tunic.','2016-11-01 01:11:49'),(9539586,168298980,3070,3841982464,39,'Philisophical Path',0,47,2,-3907,-677,'The Philosophical Path is a pillar of representation for those traditions established by pratice of spiritualists. In their name the Alliance University will focus on metaphysical practice and exploration. Delving the depths of the mind, body, and spirit connection unique to entities within the city of dreams. ','2016-07-23 21:39:18'),(12718384,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(9539622,168298980,3070,3841982464,39,'Academic path',0,47,2,-3896,-687,'The Academic path formerly known as the Quill is a pillar of representation for those proud traditions of teaching dreamers to pursue knowledge in all things. it is in this path that the Alliance will focus on secular and scholarly pursuits, restoration and advancement.','2016-07-23 21:44:41'),(12718383,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(12718382,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(10781714,4278716904,2884,3338665984,42,'Vistael\'s Chaks',0,21,16,-1922,-2803,'Not sure what he want\'s to do with them. I\'ll find out and remove them asap\'ly. ~L~','2016-12-23 08:40:29'),(12718381,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(9663474,856164840,4000551,1308622848,2842663,'4th Sphere',0,21,30,11542,-12289,'Decide between KoES and the Peace Corpse. Regardless of your decision, each group is in need of some exposure. If KoES, lead a project that displays their shadow like characteristics for the City to see. If you choose the Peace Corpse, negotiate 4 new contracts and see them each to their end. Report the details upon completion.','2016-08-08 04:15:14'),(9539588,168298980,3070,3841982464,39,'The Star Knights',0,47,2,-3917,-668,'The Starknights is (Militia of the) Alliance University, which embodies the old spirit of honor and justice itself. The Starnights will use their strength and conviction to protect those of the Alliance, the innocents within the city of dreams. Preserving the dream for future generations of dreamers. Truth, Honor, Knowledge, its ten','2016-07-23 21:40:50'),(9635923,66041,16777983,0,0,'Ruberto',0,18,26,8840,-17582,'Ruberto wears a pure white cotton t-shirt that doesn\'t appear to ever take on a stain - No dirt nor sticky substance will adhere to it.  He wears a blue denim set of overhauls that have a small pocket in the front that always holds a flower of varying colors, the likes of which changes based on the mood of the person carrying him.  The rest of teh doll appears finely fashioned with great detail.','2016-08-04 16:00:04'),(9931729,4127721956,6818814,2751463424,2562090,'Bequeath - Learn',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'You are now the spirit of giving and if we must say, the only one who knows what dreamers truly want in their dreams.  Take some time and give dreamers something you think they need (This could be words, actions..anything, serious or not, be creative.)  Take note of who you bless with your giving nature, what was given and how they responded.  I look forward to your report.\r\n','2016-09-10 00:04:32'),(12719088,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,44,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:22'),(12719087,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,44,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:22'),(9582066,386402788,3070,2281701376,42,'Forge Colours',0,41,2,-516,-4046,'The colour information contained herin comes from Hikari X.   Each focus has four colours they may use for the PRIMARY colour when forging.  These are as follows:  DS - Blood, Teal, Tan, Plum   GK - Jade, Azure, Beige, Chalk   FS - Night, Sand, Abyss, Gold    SM - Cyan, Berry, Earth, Fire','2016-07-29 02:28:20'),(9893214,4178053608,3345185,1023410176,2561835,'Inz - NMF (10)',0,47,9,-4752,3488,'Release your inner emphant! Use Nightmare Form in front of other dreamers and play out the part, then continue to do so for a few minutes after its effect have run out until you can observe reactions! You may discharge yourself from any suspicion of insanity by admitting afterwards this was for a task. Report when you are satisfied with the confusion caused.','2016-09-05 06:11:23'),(9579624,1711802852,3070,570425344,39,'WordSmith Oath',0,41,3,-3228,-5292,'I, [name], hereby swear to uphold the duties of the WordSmiths and honor the written word. I promise to keep the integrity of my Mark in tact, and to never present a known falsehood as truth within my writing. I understand that this is both an honor and obligation, and will not seek to use this Mark to elevate myself above others.','2016-07-28 18:30:26'),(9590037,4278716900,1838078,385875968,2624039,'Drain Self 50',0,41,19,-3354,269,'I would like for you to gather info about both Zaxun and Xun\'rok then hold a big debate on them. I don\'t want you to be biased on it at all. I want good and bad about both. If it is an early gathering, then I would like to have notes posted up on the open scrolls because I can\'t be there most days. I want this to be debatable. Posted up for all to attend.','2016-07-30 04:54:55'),(12719085,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,44,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:22'),(9587277,4144499176,1510200,419430400,2624039,'Forge-50',0,41,19,-3424,232,'Simplicity is key. In the simplest of terms, I want you to teach others to be simple in their creations. Lead either one class of at least 6 dreamers or instruct ten individual students. Your students cannot consist of just dreamers from one House. Keep track of the instructions you gave and bring me the three best items that were created by your pupils. ','2016-07-29 19:51:53'),(9589808,2835876324,1903614,4026531840,2624040,'Abjure to 60',0,41,19,-3424,231,'Your house has been through a rough beginning. I wish for you to help strip away the \"evil\" facade that comes with someone wearing the crest. Why do you think other houses do not like KoES? You are to be the beacon of light and speaker of the house to the City. It will not be an easy job to get others to see your house in a new light. Also, I wish for you to assist with the recent loss of prime strength. Trap for the house the amount of 15k to help strengthen the Heart of the Shadow. **A**','2016-07-30 04:15:36'),(9590291,2282228196,3070,2063597568,39,'Immortality 1',0,19,32,-4587,-16487,'Not really. OfF was here though. Nice digs!\r\n','2016-07-30 05:38:45'),(9624599,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-5',0,41,10,-2554,-9460,'Bashir began his rise, and his cult formed and created terror around the city.... Me being the dreamer I am I HAD to do something about it... I formed the Wolf Pack, a group of warriors who would band together, teach dreamers how to defend themselves and stand up against Bashir and his cult.. We were strong back then.. Many many members, we never wanted a house.. Our pack was happy in the Arena. Dar\'canon, Krodoc, Pamelar, Xyn Rhade, Em\'et, so many dreamers from back in idoaclesia, they were all apart of -','2016-08-03 08:55:40'),(9822800,856164836,3070,1191182336,40,'Order of Light (4)',0,47,2,-3970,465,'role. We are very active within the community, aiding those we see are worthy of it. ','2016-08-27 21:08:09'),(12719156,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,46,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:24'),(10399779,252185064,2843,922746880,43,'Invis to 20 ',0,47,3,3245,1149,'Invis allows us to hide in plain sight. I want you to write a story about someone who felt invisible, no matter where they were, with or without the art. Why did they feel that way. Was there a way that they were able to make it better ? I look forward to hearing your report.','2016-11-07 01:20:14'),(9624531,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey',0,41,10,-2552,-9521,'It all began my first night in the forest after my brother killed our family.. I remember falling asleep inside of bushes and then waking up in this city... It all seemed so real.. I met a few dreamers who\'s names I don\'t recollect, however introductions were made.. I remember heading out to the Mt. Seeing dreamers dueling, and laughing questing... Being the warrior that I am I couldn\'t help but throw myself in the spars! I remember for months, and months I would spar every single day...\r\n','2016-08-03 08:37:49'),(9614893,520620516,3070,2080374784,39,'Note',0,47,6,-2738,5924,'These are prototypes meant for the collection of firestorm and poison. A method of creating explosive gas was stumbled upon during an experiment to create the base componants needed in the creation of a fledgling art. ','2016-08-02 02:03:13'),(9786326,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Sixth Tenant',0,21,30,11553,-12464,'\"The world is a stage for promotion\" : You should always be aware of your environment; most especially social. For there is always an opportunity to promote or advance the name and goals of the Peace Corpse. Take full advantage of these opportunities when they arise for the moment your name or cause has become the news of yesterday, you are already forgotten.','2016-08-23 00:05:11'),(9624565,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-3',0,41,10,-2557,-9492,'nothing about it.. and they were right.. Our city, idoaclesia had many many, beautiful women Elders... I was young! I had no idea how to contain my raging hormones back then, hahahah! The Elders did not care however.. For some reason they refused to teach me simply because of my brash nature.. I did not let that stop me however, to hell with the Elders, they won\'t be able to stop me from progressing forever! I continued to train and train and train... My skills were rising and soon I was able to beat my -','2016-08-03 08:47:41'),(9624600,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-6',0,41,10,-2554,-9446,'the wolf pack in some type of way... Those days, were the best days of my dreams.. Soon my peers started to hate my competitve nature however... and their pranks started turning into bullying... I pleaded with them to stop... I told them they know I can\'t do anything about it so stop picking on me.. They didn\'t care.. Blind, Deafen, Scare.. You name it, it was cast on me, even at random times out of the blue! How many times must I beg them to stop bullying me? My mind went mad with rage... ','2016-08-03 08:59:27'),(9624632,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-7',0,41,10,-2552,-9432,'I just couldn\'t take it anymore... At this point of my dreams the city had taken out multiple enemies, Bashir, Dynroth, some other crazy stuff... They handle their asses alright.. But this enemy.. He was different... His name was the Shadow Lord.. He would take over our entire thresholds and turn them into pure darkness, and in these rooms there was no sanctuary.. He was powerful beyond belief basically... I had enough of their bullying me.. I ran to the Shadow Lord one evening in front of Trisha Pawm and-','2016-08-03 09:02:21'),(9624532,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-2',0,41,10,-2555,-9507,'You might not believe it, but I wasn\'t very good back then, HA! Sylas Prium, Ash, Kereal, they would beat the hell out of me every single day, over and over again, and I would just keep comin\' and comin\' I didn\'t care all I wanted to do was be the greatest warrior in the city, and I told them that faithfully! Back then.. The city loved me.. but my brash behavior did not sit well for too long.. Soon they no longer cared if I was unsphered, they would cast scare on me, deafen.. Blind.. They knew I could do -','2016-08-03 08:41:39'),(12718379,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(9624665,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Lu Chao\'s Journey-9',0,41,10,-2552,-9404,'without control of my own avatar and collapsed many of them all by myself.. I was collapsed and after that.. I had no more ability to dream... The Shadow Lord had taken my avatar hostage, it was no longer mine.. All I saw was darkness as I tried to dream.. Trapped in an abyss of shadows.. Until... The Underlight revealed itself... ---- To Be Continued...','2016-08-03 09:10:35'),(9635922,66105,16777983,0,0,'Lady Patches',0,18,26,7683,-17503,'Small princess doll. Her hair is well brushed and looked after, and is a deep shade of abyss. The hair waves hair with a single piece swept up. A small princess tiara made of platinum rests upon her head, a single sapphire is set in the center. Flanked on both sides are smaller gems of azure. She wears a silken plum dress that is adorned with glittering stars of various sizes. When squeezed, from her heart you hear her says, \"Wish.\" Her beautiful night colored eyes sparkle. ><','2016-08-04 15:58:21'),(9646360,4261939688,1510213,637534208,2579751,'Tember: Forge 50',0,18,31,16561,-6317,'You are to hold classes on battle tactics. These are to be one on one classes, a private lesson if you will. You are to create the supplies with which your students will be learning from. You are to teach them how to be effective in battle, able to stand toe to toe with the most powerful of enemies and remain coherent for an extended period of time. You must actually impart some form of knowledge, not just watch them practice shooting a chakram.','2016-08-06 01:19:24'),(9646025,67635684,9374718,570425344,2639655,'Misdirection 10',0,47,6,-3509,5862,'How can we Misdirect our enemies in such a way that would benefit us? Think up a rumor to be spread by your choice of medium: the gossip columnist, stray forged notes, word of mouth, etc. Keep an eye on how fast it spreads and the impact it had. Have fun and report back how things went!','2016-08-06 00:34:41'),(9663303,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Freedom of Speech',0,41,2,-195,-3853,'Freedom of Speech is often discussed topic. As honorable as this sounds, we do not live in a dream of full free speech. There are some topics which are socially unacceptable and should never be mentioned or acted on. We should never harass anyone based on cultural upbringing, orientation, gender or sexually. These are frowned upon and often acted on by dreamer and elder alike. There... ','2016-08-08 03:38:16'),(9761656,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling!3',0,41,10,-2104,-9792,'Vill was inexpirenced as he never used blast in a war before, but his partner was a master in it and taught him a few choice ideal ways of using it in battle. As the teams were ready and insight elems were plentiful, the other focus\'s went up to the upper areas to watch....','2016-08-19 21:47:34'),(9786293,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Fourth Tenant',0,21,30,11548,-12430,'\"All for one, and one for all\" : Every goal that the Peace Corpse seeks to achieve is for the betterment of all members of the community. Your individual goals are the task of the entire community to help you attain. All members bring something unique to the Peace Corpse and it is from this uniqueness that we are stronger than others. Walk your dreams knowing that everything you achieve, we all achieve, and that the goals of the many benefit the few just as prominently.','2016-08-23 00:01:32'),(10221182,4278716900,1903614,385875968,2699559,'Abjure 40',0,47,5,-3024,3865,'Strip down the art itself and find me things around the City that could make up this art. This could be herbs, minerals, items found around the City. I would gather this art would take many things to make up the ability to use it.','2016-10-16 06:44:44'),(10446552,134744552,9636673,2063597568,2639655,'Channel - Flower',0,47,6,-3509,5862,'I want you to find a room with a number of dreamers and strike up a conversation.  Then evoke random and change speech patterns, topic of conversation, and to whom you are addressing.  Do this three times in a conversation and see if others pick up on what you are doing.\r\n','2016-11-12 21:56:21'),(9663372,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Freedom of Speech 2',0,41,2,-184,-3865,'is also the art of DreamStrike. Any discussion on the matter is sure to rile up emotion. A more accurate term would be \"modified\" free speech....and with good reason! You have a brain, use it before you speak!','2016-08-08 03:45:59'),(10375844,4127721956,9571326,2751463424,2576938,'Rally - Mini',0,47,12,5627,6583,'Help rally your members by contributing to at least one project that your house members are currently working on.\r\n','2016-11-04 03:33:13'),(10375974,2198342116,9571326,4261412864,2576937,'Rally Mini-Thunder',0,47,12,5627,6584,'This art has SO many phenominal uses, but lacks a symbol or appropriately epic music.  So, I would like you to write a short Anthem for the House that we could use to really announce our presence when we choose to march en-mass.','2016-11-04 03:47:56'),(9869022,520620516,3070,1610612736,43,'Loyalty',0,21,30,11568,-12860,'Message to the future. Your loyalty is the Peace Corpse first. Dont forget. Dont get caught up in house politics. We started from the bottom, now we here.','2016-09-02 06:54:52'),(9678428,2835876324,3476478,4026531840,2576936,'Train to 70',0,47,12,5699,6579,'This task is two fold. I wish for you to use your halo to task multiple students in ways to rid the City of Revenants as well as our two \"guests\". The second part is that I wish for you to work on your arts. You will rais e5 of the arts that you have at 9, to at least 20. Use your Train Self if needed. **A**','2016-08-10 02:59:42'),(9678567,2835876324,1641470,4026531840,2699560,'Restore -- 50 ',0,47,5,-2887,3862,'Restoration plans are often difficult and time consuming. Having said that, I wish for you to ponder something that the City is in desperate need of assistance. That can be a reinvention or a complete restoration. Often times the simplest fix is to infuse something with passion. Think of two things to help heal and think of ways to do just that. Find me when you have a well thought out process. Make your efforts worthy of the reward you seek. **A**','2016-08-10 03:16:19'),(12719371,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(9678727,940050920,4197181,2063597568,2576935,'Invisible 60 ',0,47,12,5725,6571,'As a dual-focus dreamer you will be the only GateKeeper to merge the insights of the invisible to the GateKeepers of the City.  I want you to work with the GateKeepers to re-establish the guild. You don\'t need to do this yourself, but you may find a way of delegating this to the other gatekeepers.  Have them set a single, specific, underlying goal that the guild shall aspire to achieve.\r\n ','2016-08-10 03:41:00'),(9778466,2835876324,1903614,4026531840,2561832,'Abjure -- 70',0,47,9,-4790,3532,'This task will be two fold. First, I wish for you to create a guidebook for the perfect use of Abjure. It should include everything about the art that you know as well as personal experiences with the art at its various levels. Secondly, I wish for you to strip the walls from yourself and share with me what lies beneath the rough surface that you have build. Expose your inner most fears and desires and we will discuss how they can be turned into strengths. Make your efforts worthy of such a high plateau. ','2016-08-22 04:10:06'),(9893899,526820,3070,637534208,43,'Painting',0,47,13,-5669,463,'*Here lies a painting of Aileron, Anasina, and Arnaya on the Little Bridge in Evernight. The bridge is beautifully remodeled and shines with a glistening green glow*','2016-09-05 08:24:08'),(9728479,4043376569,3254780671,0,0,'Immortal Dreams IX',0,2,31,10309,-10205,'A page, three iron bound holes at its top. Written over the page in a precise hand are individual runes, glowing blood red creating an aura that surrounds the entire page.','2016-08-16 01:34:55'),(10205686,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,8703,-4246,'','2016-10-14 02:35:55'),(12719370,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719369,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719368,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719367,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(9718874,1325926884,3070,1744830464,39,'Vampiric Draw (I)c',0,41,5,-141,-6819,'between Umbric\'s spiritual forces and a new batch of dreamers coming to settle and rebuild in the City of Underlight. The art works like an undetected leech - sucking the life out of a single target, formulated by supernatural gifts and unique Soul-maniuplation by the Umbric Defenders.. similar to how they envisioned outsiders themselves... sucking the life out of their plane.  - V\r\n','2016-08-14 21:14:59'),(9932300,526820,3070,637534208,43,'The Hotai Plague 3',0,41,10,-2309,-9556,'Some dreamers gained a type of minor immunity and would not transform further. It was a painful experience. As they transformed they lost their minds, They were \"Hotai\". Dreamers didn\'t like the beasts and began hunting as they didn\'t understand or trust the newfound beasts. Everytime they collapsed, they released the spore into the air. ','2016-09-10 01:43:38'),(12719224,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,47,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:25'),(9761641,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling! 2',0,41,10,-2131,-9791,'He set the date, and time, and Seers from many diffrent backgrounds gathered for their very first blast compitions.  They were delgated into teams of 2 for each side. Vill being a younger dreamer who just earlier the night before learned blast was paired up with a high sphered Blast Artist, of a diffrent house.','2016-08-19 21:44:29'),(9761701,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling! 6',0,41,10,-2022,-9789,'... However his partner used that opportunity of Vill being taken out to finish the last blows on the two remaining opposing teams, until it was time for the last two teams to compete for the crown and prize!, this was the hardest team, and although Vill\'s team got 2nd place, it was a great prize and memory the city has not seen before!','2016-08-19 21:55:47'),(9718101,2215119332,3070,2013265920,40,'Small Chakrams',0,22,27,-4879,-17433,'Very low-level Chakrams for Experimental purposes or for Unsphered members.  - Blue','2016-08-14 19:15:15'),(9924880,4278716900,3070,3338665984,42,'Shadow\'d Beliefs 1',0,47,2,-2836,426,'We believe: 1) The Dream to be an alternative state of consciousness; a World between that of the Material & the Spiritual, which is a stepping stone to achieving Balance. 2) The Dream has an effect on both worlds. We do this for our own Spiritual evolution. 3) Order is the positive & Chaos is the negative forces. For us, both are relative to our existance. The Shadow is the combination of the two. To achieve true Balance, one must be open to experiencing the extremes of each ... and both. (con\'t)','2016-09-09 03:07:05'),(9967906,1124600292,3070,637534208,43,'Return Notes: Lyra2',0,41,5,1035,-6258,'We will probably never know of the great dreamer which created it.  History remembers only the name of the great GateKeeper which added this powerful art to the Major GateKeeper Arts, it was Askold, (apprentice to Retvizan). he also researched this art and upgraded it. As a result, it now allows teleportation in each location. It formerly was only to house. Now history will remember his efforts forever. ','2016-09-14 03:12:34'),(9739213,654838248,1641303,1493172224,2561835,'Dina, Healer',0,47,9,-4922,3545,'Find two locations where the Revenants are able to cross into this City. Discover why they are able to pass the veil. Utilizing the assistance of others you are to lead them in repairing whatever it is that has been broken. The how is up to you, the strength of your attempt comes from those you lead. Lead them well.','2016-08-17 04:52:29'),(9941558,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Kinesis History 2',0,41,10,-2429,-9617,'The man began evoking DreamStrike, her cries while being seperated from her husband, were heartbreaking. She knew at this moment she could do nothing. But then her hands began glowing brightly with willpower, and to her avail, she began evoking a new art! Her anger and Will knocked the striker back and cancelled the evoke! Thus was the first evocation of the art of kinesis. ','2016-09-11 01:08:34'),(12719223,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,47,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:25'),(9746855,520620516,3070,1610612736,43,'The Peace Corpse',0,21,30,11566,-12844,'On this 17th of August 2016, the Peace Corpse took this house of PoR as its stronghold.','2016-08-18 03:57:14'),(9747520,654838248,1706843,1493172224,2699563,'They See You Weavin',0,47,5,-2833,3862,'Organize a group of Dreamers and go forth out into the City. Identify areas of weakness within the City\'s walls and develop a means of fortifying them. You are then to put your theories to the test and into practice. You never know what may slip into the City when the walls that protect you weaken. ~There is a drawing of a stick figure, with quite large circles drawn out to the side of what would be a torso~','2016-08-18 05:52:55'),(9889119,151521764,3070,1023410176,43,'AoE Beliefs 3',0,22,30,10072,-10477,'While lesser mares may contain trapped souls, we do not believe that the soul is kept within the essence. Any soul is released upon the mare\'s collapse, leaving behind only the essence of the mare.\r\nDarkmares and Datoken are an awakened creature and sentient. Their awakening process is a mystery and is suspected to be corrupted. Be this by design, or accident is unknown and a subject of research.\r\nWe abide by the tenets of Truth, Honor and Understanding. The three circles in our emblem symbolize these.','2016-09-04 16:07:53'),(9761601,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling! 1',0,41,10,-2154,-9788,'One eventful duel after the next, the dreamers of this city gathered to hone their skills in blade and chak, until one unique dreamer of the Seer persuation had a thought occur to him. With all these seers around and newlies who have barely obtained the whitfull art of Blast, why not hold a Blast Duel Compitition with Rewards!?','2016-08-19 21:42:15'),(12719222,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,47,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:25'),(9786292,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Third Tenant',0,21,30,11555,-12406,'\"My companions before the stranger\" : There are few bonds greater than family save those which we create for ourselves. The Peace Corpse is a community where the goals of all members, both individual and joint, become the goals of all. To this end, no other dreamer should come before a fellow member of the Peace Corpse. Always seek to defend your fellows no matter the situation. Only the strength of our unity will allow us to prevail and attain the heights we seekt to achieve, and surpass.','2016-08-22 23:59:33'),(9755961,526820,3070,486539264,40,'Revenant painting',0,47,13,-8284,439,'a pastel paiting featuring 3 bikini clad Revenant female dreamers in the beachy sand area of Albino caves, the sun is shown shining brightly as well as a beach ball and Bamra chasing the ball in the background with one of the Revenants sunbathing the one of the left waving towards you with a scary grin','2016-08-19 08:33:04'),(12719366,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(9960167,4278716900,68606,385875968,2564647,'JP - Mini',0,47,12,5079,6524,'For a couple days, I want you to go around and act like JP helps keeping you under control from ______. You fill in the blank, make it fun and entertaining.','2016-09-13 07:03:59'),(9761667,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling! 4',0,41,10,-2077,-9790,'Vill watched as 3 seperate teams battled throughout the entire arena, even using the stairs and running throughout the crowds and crowded room blasting away sometimes blasting the wrong dreamers on accident. the tallys were coming out on who was winning....','2016-08-19 21:49:39'),(9944156,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Peace Market Items',0,21,30,12103,-13164,'The Items that are behind this codex belong to the Peace Market.. They are to be sold at the auction, so do keep them in mint condition when looking at it and placing it back down? Thanks, comrades!  -Captain Lu Chaos','2016-09-11 08:51:16'),(9761700,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Blast Dueling! 5',0,41,10,-2049,-9788,'Vill got very excited as his team was up for his very first blast duel, he decided to mostly avoid being blasted, and even with his lower level blast he did well to try to avoid the attacks from the two diffrent powerful seers he was up against!, the crowd cheered! Vill was soon enough taken out and collpased however as the two others were quick and expirenced!','2016-08-19 21:53:32'),(9889716,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Kinesis - Learn',0,33,22,292,22546,'This task is for Willbur*cough*, for the art of Kinesis. This art has been my saving grace in many situations in the short time I\'ve had it. Learn the history of the art of Kinesis. Then come up with a few situations where you can safely use this art in and out of combat. ','2016-09-04 18:19:20'),(12719365,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(9787192,654838248,9243483,1493172224,2562091,'Kailee\'s Hot Air',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'You claim to have had a hand in the creation of this art? Tell me about it, how was this accomplished? What did you do? What was done after you were no longer helping? How was it completed? Also the basic information about the art itself.','2016-08-23 03:11:06'),(9770556,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Recharged!',0,21,23,6045,-5411,'These are your items that have been recharged, grab what\'s yours!','2016-08-21 02:48:40'),(9770555,3506964964,3070,1308622848,40,'Recharge',0,21,23,6240,-5232,'These items here are needing to be recharged.\r\n','2016-08-21 02:48:00'),(9959961,1325926884,3070,335544320,43,'Plaque: Void Box',0,47,14,-9981,3542,'A plaque sits made of simple stone, reading, \"This box was created in Idaoclesian times, as a cure option for the Beast Plague. The function was to draw in the energies from the plague and prevent them from entering the water during cleansing rituals.\"','2016-09-13 06:30:13'),(12719364,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10164912,688392680,3410737,4194304000,2639657,'Locate ~ 10',0,47,6,-3509,5862,'What is the point of Locate when all the people we care about can be found with House Members?  I mean seriously, why would we associate with other houses.  Isn\'t family the most important thing?  Create a story or poem that answers these questions.  Share as you are most comfortable. ','2016-10-08 22:59:03'),(10694930,2047347176,6556479,3338665984,2566954,'All Together Now!',0,47,11,5924,4157,'The 1st item chosen in a Combine is important, but won\'t work without the follow-up item. Sometimes we need to take 2nd chair. Gather your courage, wit & patience & find it in yourself to join in with OffKilter\'s efforts to work on our talisman abilities. Can work with him alone, but Combine your knowledge with his somehow. ~Lacie~','2016-12-13 05:16:08'),(9941495,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Kinesis History 1',0,41,10,-2413,-9617,'Though the names are unknown this is a recalled History by Thunderman: It was long ago in a battle in Chasm of Souls when a married couple, that ruled edgeward stronghold were ambushed by a warring house. It was a brutal assault. The female gatekeeper and her husband were cornered, her husband ended up being collapsed. ','2016-09-11 01:04:57'),(10127241,1711802856,2034466,1627389952,2562345,'What\'s the Cure?',0,41,23,-3108,2892,'I grow somewhat bitter in my old age.. I see a lot of idiocy around here. Create some sort of cure for this moronic behavior and approach your intended targets with it... tell then what you are curing them of and why.  ~c','2016-10-04 03:47:20'),(9917772,66873,3254780671,0,0,'Corrupted Essence',0,17,25,-200,-12931,'The soul essence has been corrupted, covered in a web of glowing red organic material.','2016-09-08 04:05:00'),(10136051,134744552,4918082,2063597568,2561831,'Mindblank 60',0,47,9,-4782,3517,'I want you to devise a way to have MindBlank interrupt Sense Dreamers.  With the population so small, it seems as though Sense is actually more viable than locate these dreams.  If mindblank suddenly interfered with Sense, how would it affect the art? Furthermore do you think this would be popular with all houses? Ask one member of each house their thoughts on what the implications would be.\r\n','2016-10-05 04:03:41'),(9921808,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Not-Terror Arts 1/3',0,47,6,-3395,6521,'\r\nName: Bolster\r\nOrbit/Cost: 45/20 Lucidity\r\nEffect: Entire Party receives a random \"boon\" effect, from the following list: Meditation, Trail, Mind Blank, Soul Shield, Resist Fear, Free Action, Protection, Vision, Antidote, or Purify. \r\nDuration: Instanteous, or 1min + 1min per plateau. \r\n\r\nName: Extrasensory\r\nOrbit/Cost: 15/5 Lucidity\r\nEffect: Receive a notification when you are located *specifically* (not by list). Tells who located you. On/Off functionality. \r\nDuration: 5min + 5min per plateau','2016-09-08 17:47:14'),(10072936,2282228196,3070,2281701376,40,'Seer Battle Plan 1',0,21,30,11534,-12635,'So we have many seers in our guild, I have compiled the list.  Ladysilver 7th sphere, BlackCloud 6th, Crystalline, 6th, Purple Lace 6th, HikariX 6th, Sublimemota 5th, Teon 4th, and me 3rd.  My battle plan is laid out from the point of view of someone entering through the portal from the Valley.  We should have four blasters on our house ledges.  On the left would be Lace and Sil, on the right ledge would be Cloud and Crystalline.  On our stairs we would have Vill, Sub, and HikarX as chak/blast deturants...','2016-09-27 05:57:34'),(9786229,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Second Tenant',0,21,30,11554,-12383,'\"My word is my bond\" : You come into life with only three virtues: your blood, your name, and your word. You are the sole custodian of your word and thus this is the only virtue you can truly lose. Your word should be your most prized possession. Give is sparingly and then uphold it once it is given. For your triumphs and failings reflect not only upon you, but your fellows as well.','2016-08-22 23:52:58'),(9786330,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Ninth Tenant',0,21,30,11510,-12513,'\"Every man has his price\" : No matter how an initial offer is received, there is always the potential for a more lucrative deal to be struck. Even if rejected, an offer can be altered to fit the specific needs of a client. Always make certain to offer a number of options as this makes an offer or contract more enticing. A satisfied client is a returning client and we should always strive to operate in a fashion that promotes the repetition of business for the Peace Corpse.','2016-08-23 00:10:47'),(9786362,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Tenth Tenant',0,21,30,11516,-12533,'\"If that is what is written, then that is what is written\" : Once a contract has been agreed upon, it is the obligation of the Peace Corpse to fulfill it to the satisfaction of our client. Always take care that your contracts are written carefully and detailed to the satisfcation of both client and Peace Corpse. Once agreed upon, the contract is in effect. You never want to be in a position where you lose out because care was not taken in your business dealings. ','2016-08-23 00:13:12'),(9786294,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Fifth Tenant',0,21,30,11557,-12447,'\"Professionalism is a way of life. Govern yourself accordingly\" : There is no excuse or blame to place on others for the loss of your professionalism whether in behavior or demeanor. There is no power that words or actions have over you unless you choose to empower them so. Rise above the pettiness of others and strive to always maintain your professionalism. The Peace Corpse should always seek to conduct itself accordingly.','2016-08-23 00:03:35'),(9786328,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Eighth Tenant',0,21,30,11528,-12493,'\"War is good for business; Peace is good for business\" : Simply put, a good businessperson finds work and opportunity no matter what political or socioeconomic situation the market happens to exist in at any given time. Adjust your business accordingly to become indepensable, and you will find that business is always available. Opportunity is out there waiting for the keen eye to recognize it, and the deft hand to pluck it for serving upon the table.','2016-08-23 00:08:46'),(9786327,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'Seventh Tenant',0,21,30,11560,-12479,'\"Knowledge equals power...and profit\" : There is a saying, \"The wise man hears profit in the wind.\" Acquire what knowledge you are able for the acquisition has its own rewards to both yourself and the community of the Peace Corpse. Hidden meaning can often be found if you are listening. Never dismiss information for a seemingly worthless comment to one person can prove invaluable to another.','2016-08-23 00:07:01'),(9889118,151521764,3070,1023410176,43,'AoE Beliefs 2',0,22,30,10046,-10492,'The stronger this connection is, the more likely the dreamer will feel some effects of the City outside the dreamstate. The shard of that person, however, is not likely to be affected in any way outside of the individual.\r\nWhile most houses manipulate essences as acts of faith, we cleanse essences as a form of refining. The Cleansing removes the chaotic energy, and leaves the primal components available to strengthen the Star, which then powers our equipment and our house projects.','2016-09-04 16:06:56'),(9822790,856164836,3070,1191182336,40,'Order of Light (1)',0,47,2,-3888,543,'The Order of Light is a blend of two previous strongholds merging together. The Order of the Sable Moon and the Dreamers of Light. It is an opensoul house, while the Order were already a mix of illuminate and freesoul dreamers the Light was strictly illuminated. An important factor that was shared by both houses is that they both imprisoned at the time of the merge. The followers of the \'original\' DoL mantra imprison for beliefs sake, taking into account the unawakened soul within an essence whereas most ','2016-08-27 21:04:42'),(9801359,69497,1058866177,0,0,'Ooze Soaked Essence',0,34,27,15065,-3553,'An agoknight essence covered in ooze.  It sticks to your hand as you pick it up.','2016-08-25 03:02:11'),(10508610,34081252,9571326,1191182336,2751016,'RallyMini-Arly',0,47,11,5327,4422,'Rally up some friends for some cause. But it has to be for some greater good, not just a drinkin party or chat sesh. Also hold it in a place where most of the people involved have to be rallied to the place you hold it so they see a place they normally wouldnt. Doesnt need to be a big ol deal, impromptu is fine, but report to me who went, where you were and what the cause was.','2016-11-20 05:35:20'),(10055432,71481,152699909,0,0,'Fallen Star',0,18,8,8196,2649,'The smoldering remains of an unknown object.','2016-09-25 01:58:41'),(9924916,4278716900,3070,3338665984,42,'Shadow\'d Beliefs 2',0,47,2,-2845,439,'4) Orbits, Spheres & Arts are all products of our own experiences. 5) the Lesser Mares are products of malicious Will & aid in dispersing InBalance. They are composed of the Elemental forces of Chaos & used to maintain Balance. Their Essences are given to the Shadow to maintain equilibrium. 6) We desire the whole Dream process to be an experience of constant evolution, creation & expansion. Our beliefs form the fundamental structure of our Dreams. To lose persective would be to unravel the City\'s fabric.','2016-09-09 03:12:53'),(9849180,4278258681,4110418436,0,0,'Claw of Mork',0,17,22,6546,5338,'A sharp powerful claw that could rip through any dream fabric rests in hand.  An intense feeling of fear takes over your very avatar.  On closer inspection, black ooze can be seen all along the jagged edges.  One of five talons from the claw are missing. ','2016-08-31 01:22:14'),(9859734,822610404,3070,922746880,43,'ode to flower',0,47,6,-3509,5862,'It bums me out to see you sad ur smile\'s been gone for days. so its my turn to cheer u up i know a thousand ways ! So lean on back and take a breath, release those worries for awhile. And maybe I can lend a hand and we\'ll reclaim ur smile. The grass was never greener, the birds sing just for u. To hell with all this drama, let\'s smash it with our shoe ! If there\'s a way that i can help, any way at all, think of me thinking about u and give my ass a call.  -u wished someone would write one for u, right ??','2016-09-01 06:39:14'),(9896040,50858468,3070,1040187392,43,'Restored Clock',0,47,13,-7415,-625,'A functional and aesthetically pleasing skeleton clock. The original golden brass structure is restored to a finely polished sheen. Worn gears have been remade and adjusted to a perfect fit. New clock hands and screws fastening the clockwork are carefully hand-tooled in steel, tempered to a royal blue color by dragon breath. The clock rests on a refinished antique wooden base. In lieu of a pendulum, an intricately carved ancient gold medal bearing a newly apposed signature on its back: \"A.Silverscale\"','2016-09-05 15:47:29'),(10205729,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,9122,-2517,'','2016-10-14 02:46:33'),(9932302,526820,3070,637534208,43,'The Hotai Plague 1',0,41,10,-2294,-9533,'It all started with a dreamer named Bandaret, he no longer has the avatar of a dreamer but formerly was a elder type dreamer with a cackle, he longed to acquire the staff Dynroth held. He was always a bit loose in the brain, but at the same time a cunning...','2016-09-10 01:46:50'),(10077974,3708291556,3070,620756992,43,'Boots',0,47,14,-9507,2212,'These boots are fortified with thick, cured Bogrom hides roughly stitched together. Despite a smell reminiscent of rotting Bog meat, the boots provides some protection. Regardless, the boots exemplifies the remarkable skill of a dedicated soldier. ','2016-09-27 22:52:38'),(9932334,526820,3070,637534208,43,'The Hotai Plague 4',0,41,10,-2320,-9567,'EA eventually decided against the collapsing and instead went with the curing method. Soon they came upon a method of removing the disease using an Obsidian box. It wasn\'t until then that this disease was defeated. ','2016-09-10 01:47:39'),(10523558,526867,333971713,177922,1538816,'Ward',0,23,3,1028,-6001,'','2016-11-22 03:01:19'),(12718377,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(9993080,65913,437060863,0,0,'Fractured Key',0,21,12,887,-18978,'A golden key, a few of the prongs snapped off and a long crack runs down its length.','2016-09-17 08:28:36'),(10007596,671615460,3070,2281701376,40,'Reweave History 2',0,41,5,445,-6919,'reweave on the other talismen as well.  After many experimentations, he found out that all the other talisman like blades, chaks, alts,elemens and their silk were all not durable enough to be considered for reweaving.  The shields on the other hand were.  As no dreamer has the capability yet to reweave our walls, the main function of Reweave has been to fix our shields and path the city walls.                         Big thanks to Purple Lace for this information.','2016-09-19 08:22:55'),(9965358,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Restore | L',0,33,22,219,22536,'It would seem that you\'ve seen it all. You are going through the motions doing these mundane tasks. I would like to \"restore\" your faith in us teachers. Consider this scenario: You are the ruler of the Darkmares, what would you do with this power? How would you treat the dream? Would you be a good ruler or evil? I expect a lot from you!','2016-09-13 18:33:13'),(9967874,1124600292,3070,637534208,43,'Return Notes: Lyra1',0,41,5,1047,-6280,'As told by Thunderman was unheard of before the Nightmare Wars, but Nightmares entered the the city, the great Combat began. Powerful commanders needed to go through long distances to come from one front to another. It took too long a time to concentrate main forces in the one battle zone, or all Great Warriors to go in House to protectit from emergency alert. In that difficult time was discovered the art of Return. ','2016-09-14 03:09:16'),(10040612,2668104168,6163234,1023410176,2676523,'Inz - Sacrifice',0,22,30,9160,-11209,'Learn of the sacrifices our House had to make in order to learn the Art. There are many records of these events on our private House boards on the City Walls, and Anasina is a great person to ask in person.','2016-09-23 06:08:27'),(9983994,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ Drowning ~',0,41,11,-7023,-2335,'I drown in an ever deepening ocean of despair. All around me seems to diminish into dark clouds of an infinitely vast vortex of gloom. My very soul cries out to the empty spaces that envelop me and echo to my own empty arms. I need to fill this space with something...someone..before I cease to exist - like a single rain drop vanishes into an endless sea.','2016-09-16 07:22:10'),(10044534,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'SS Vs. M. Blank - 1',0,41,17,-5762,-133,'I believe Soul Shield affects Mind Blank, and Mind Blank only, due to the specific natures of these two arts. When you apply Soul Shield, you can tell that you are being protected from the Chaos, right? Well, it stands to reason, then, that Mind Blank induces some sort of chaos upon the target. It follows my theory that chaos is a different form of Dreamsoul -- Mind Blank uses the same energies that Locate Dreamer uses, except it inverts it into its more chaotic state. ','2016-09-23 19:46:13'),(10077173,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Pulling Arts - 3',0,47,6,-3440,6280,'\r\n5.) Tug; Will; Orbit 70; Cost: 40 Will\r\nEffect: All unmoving dreamers in a given room begin to slowly move toward the evoker, for a duration of 20 seconds, plus 20 per plateau. Moving dreamers experience a Kinesis effect, once every 5 seconds, pushing them toward the evoker. ','2016-09-27 20:13:03'),(10226688,2198342116,3070,4261412864,41,'Arnaya\'s',0,41,8,263,-8882,'Arnaya\'s contribution to the novel study contest.\r\n','2016-10-16 19:42:13'),(10013601,4127721956,6949886,2751463424,2562090,'PC - 20',0,47,6,-3619,5644,'One of your fellow members still needs to get back some much needed energy from returning the city.  Since you see him often why not come up with a game that will encourage him and yourself to gain at least an orbit or so.  (Games can be done even smacking the sham, be creative)  When you report describe the game and tell me how much hunting you got done!  I look forward to the report.\r\n','2016-09-19 22:40:52'),(10030672,3876063716,3148798,4160749568,2564647,'Jade - Push',0,47,12,5076,6490,'(Support Task): Push yourself to explore something that needs pushing. Forge me something that can do the pushing job required, and show me its mechanics! Ensure a thorough report. ','2016-09-22 05:01:21'),(10016249,1913129448,6097758,1493172224,2564651,'Rubber and Glue',0,47,12,4994,6324,'You\'re one of those... wordy people. Hold a class about the downfalls as well as the joy of the written word. How can words be used to disparage as well as to lift up? Require written examples of what people learned from you.','2016-09-20 07:16:13'),(10077939,1057491428,3070,620756992,43,'Radiant Blade',0,47,13,-8542,-667,'This weapon is truly a fine piece of workmanship. Intricate organic carvings intertwine along the hilt, enclosing an exquisitely beautiful gem, almost as if it were an eye gazing calmly back at you. Indeed, every now and then out of the corner of your eye you almost catch it blinking.','2016-09-27 22:40:33'),(10039421,4043835876,3070,1308622848,39,'Dynroth\'s Devices 2',0,47,13,-5662,622,'devices were taken back by Dynroth. Bandaret, upset by this move, stole the devices back and used them to come to the variant known as Idoaclesia. Dynroth followed not long after, contracting the Eternal Order to find the devices in exchange for a reward. ','2016-09-23 03:31:50'),(10039420,4043835876,3070,1308622848,39,'Dynorth\'s Devices 1',0,47,13,-5668,595,'Dynroth had a student named Bandaret that sought to learn of Dynroth\'s ability to pass from variant to variant of the City. Bandaret was a teacher, and Dynroth sought the ability of Train. Taking Bandaret as his student he agreed to crafted a set of devices that allowed Bandaret the ability to do what Dynroth did naturally in exchange for the art of Train. This is how the Refitted Talisman and Oddly Shaped device came to be. They were held by Bandaret for only a short time until he upset Dynroth and the...','2016-09-23 03:30:40'),(10080187,526824,2832,922746880,43,'Codex',0,18,18,11202,-12095,'Can someone please recharge these ? they\'re 11 levels low but all that i have right now','2016-09-28 05:30:40'),(10039926,2852653540,3070,402653184,39,'Kailee\'s',0,17,30,12070,-9418,'You touch, you die!','2016-09-23 04:20:24'),(10039924,2852653540,3070,402653184,39,'Kailee\'s',0,17,8,7013,-7838,'You touch, you die!','2016-09-23 04:19:31'),(12717642,1493239752,570622478,0,0,'Plum Teal Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10044535,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'SS Vs. M. Blank - 2',0,41,17,-5768,-95,'So when someone uses Locate Dreamer to find you, your Mind Blank uses that chaos to meet and counteract the eneriges of Locate Dreamer. The Locater can tell that their locate was intercepted, and thus knows that their target is dreaming, but cannot tell where, because the energies of Locate Dreamer were never returned. Soul Shield creates a bubble of anit-chaos in the same way that Mind Blank creates a bubble of anti-Locate Dreamer. Thusly, someone Soul Shielded can neither Mind Blank, nor be Mind Blanked.','2016-09-23 19:49:14'),(10735833,4485,13437953,0,0,'KoES Flag',0,24,11,580,-12043,'','2016-12-18 02:52:46'),(10118966,4278716900,3070,805306368,39,'Angel of dreams pt1',0,41,11,-6081,-2638,'alone in the time of darkness, the time of blackness\r\ndemons of the night awake, bringing with them my fears\r\napprehension\r\nconcern\r\ntrepidation\r\nsurrounding me, they drag me toward\r\nthe mire of all that scares me\r\npanic\r\nfear \r\nacceptance\r\na light cuts through the darkness, shining like a vision\r\nbringing with it a sense of warmth\r\nconfusion\r\nlonging\r\ndesire\r\n','2016-10-03 00:26:21'),(10101538,520620516,3070,805306368,39,'fatesender totem',0,21,16,-2545,-3351,'In your hand rests a small object, surface smooth like glass and darker than a moonless night sky, carved from a knot of a venerable tree.  The animal\'s body appears tense as he stands with ears up, snout slightly raised, and his tongue lolling as if smiling at some unknown thought.  An ancient trickster is known for his stealth and humor, combined with his ability to disrupt even the most calm of circumstances.  His eyes gleam as the light catches the facets of rubies inlaid into his face.  He is Coyote. ','2016-09-30 20:22:29'),(10818739,4026536613,13437953,0,0,'Fighting Policy',0,47,1,459,-301,'There will be NO fighting in the Library, Teaching Guild or the adjacent halls. If you are found to be in violation of this policy, you will be placed on a train ban for a specific amount of time. Should further violations occur during this time, stronger action will be taken. Escalating arguments will not be tolerated while teaching is occurring. You will be asked to leave the area.               **HeadMaster Akkadian**','2016-12-28 04:16:44'),(10077240,285739496,5901105,3087007744,2641449,'Shield ',0,21,30,12564,-12524,'Confidential -  You have oft spoken of being our shield...our protector.  Do not go out of  your way or be obvious, but get the one who is a thorn in my side. ++SC++','2016-09-27 20:31:31'),(10072938,2282228196,3070,2281701376,40,'Seer Battle Plan 2',0,21,30,11548,-12674,'against dreamers trying to come over and chak our ledge blasters.  In the main facade we could have two or three seers there to help keep the attention of the attackers.  It would be either me and teon, or another from the stair crew.  Our main job would to be to keep the  attackers on the main floor and away from our blasters on the ledges. We would run around chak/blast to try and keep their attention. With this defense we could easily take down a group of 4 to 5 well armed and decently sphered dreamers.','2016-09-27 06:04:25'),(10077940,4278716900,3070,620756992,43,'Shadowed Staff',0,47,13,-8574,-599,'Before your very eyes, dark and weird runes shift slightly on this deadly weapon. This object bears the markings of an ancient civilization . An inscription reads \"...the master of the storm must withstand his strongest enemy... himself...\"','2016-09-27 22:44:05'),(10077941,235407844,3070,620756992,43,'Glass Clock',0,47,14,-9502,2237,'In your hand rests a copper-edged clock. The glass feels surreally cool in your hand. Nearly four inches from top to bottom, this glimmering clock of polished glass is of the highest quality. You see the mark of a Dreamwrght master inscribed on the wooden handle.','2016-09-27 22:46:04'),(10205689,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7723,-3955,'','2016-10-14 02:36:16'),(10079928,856164840,2869,1308622848,39,'Protection mini',0,47,12,5075,6439,'As GK Masters, we are to help protect the future of the Keeper focus by progressing ourselves and our fellow GKs. Out of the current dreaming GKs, I myself can only think of 3 potential candidates for apprenticeship, and I\'m not sure how I feel about apprenticing Lu Chaos. Guage the Keepers, unordained, and bring me your feedback.','2016-09-28 04:43:08'),(10228024,4144499176,6556482,419430400,2751015,'Combine-Mini',0,47,11,5327,4421,'Come up with an idea for how we could Combine minis together. Train self to 80 is such a terrible thing that we should have a means to bypass the middle man in some regards!','2016-10-16 23:27:05'),(10111331,1325926884,3070,335544320,43,'Plaque',0,47,14,-9432,2844,'A plaque of red gold reads, \"9/7/16: On this night, Zaxun attempted a ritual to weaken the sanctuaries. On this night, the City stood as one, no matter what crest they wore, and fought against this, be it by fighting Zaxun head on, snatching away the ritual focus, or repairing the Gold Sanctuary and keeping it from falling. This earring is a token reminder that dreamers can have many strengths, but it is when we all stand together as one that we are strongest.\"','2016-10-01 23:22:11'),(12719363,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10088169,285739496,4000550,3087007744,2827561,'All About the Focus',0,21,30,12571,-12543,'First, a lively gathering  /debate on focus stereotypes.. have some questions ready for attendees..etc.. Second.. another gathering..\"New Focus Showcase!\" people make up a new focus..tell about them..what they would do, learn, be known for...etc.. Have fun. ++SC++','2016-09-29 01:59:39'),(10088433,1141377512,2874,3338665984,42,'Fried Green Pickles',0,21,16,-2545,-3372,'Fried Green Pickles all the way! Fried Green Pickles here to stay! To fry the Pickle to shiney glaze? Stick up the back, and set to Blaze! Rotate often, this ye must, or Pickle screams & causes fuss! Round \'n Round a\'firey Blaze, Fried Green Pickles, all the rage! ~Lacie~','2016-09-29 02:55:02'),(10188958,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ Hopeless ~',0,41,11,-7043,-2384,'The hunger looms still, to fill the empty void in these dreams. Desolate despair behind a cheery smile, the master of disguise continues on, running out of masks, running out of time...','2016-10-12 00:28:00'),(10092923,336071140,3070,637534208,43,'Ode to Sorsha 3',0,21,16,-3146,-3873,'Now a bit about Sorsha. You know she hated the idea of War, and that hate will remain with me forever. What has kept her going was her passion, commitment and love for her friends; their reflections, their feelings, and the power to uplift one another above normal things. She taught me a valuable lesson, that if there is anything worth fighting for, it is the right to follow our own paths to this goal and to prevent our future newlies  from having their souls ripped from existance by forces of malign.','2016-09-29 17:48:29'),(12717641,17041480,131859,10767,0,'Blood Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10221716,4027058664,2838,922746880,43,'Antidote to 30',0,47,3,3190,1151,'Uthanatos, for this task I\'d like you to create an entirely new history of the art of antidote. Write it as if no current history exists. I\'d like to see a decent story with the added  elements of  precisely why and how the art was created. Serious or entertaining, I\'ll leave it completely up to you. I look forward to hearing your result.','2016-10-16 08:25:24'),(10111299,1325926884,3070,335544320,43,'Plaque',0,47,14,-9953,3571,'The plaque reads. \"The Cycloynx was an Idaoclesian windmill designed to attempt to bring seasons to Idaoclesia. It also contained a rather effective forging apparatus within it. It was made by Vampyro and named by Jade.\"','2016-10-01 23:19:09'),(10104412,4127721956,592894,2751463424,2564650,'Prot - Mini Jade',0,47,12,5083,6467,'You are now charged with giving out \"protection\" to the citizens of the city.  What that protection takes the form of is up to you (be creative) when you give a dreamer some \"protection\" give them your patented slogan (have fun with it!) I look forward to hearing your protection, slogans and who you gave it to!  Good Luck.\r\n','2016-10-01 05:52:51'),(12719362,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10293429,4127721956,1707006,2751463424,2561834,'Reweave Mini - Dina',0,47,9,-4739,3319,'Come up with a theory that could utilize reweave as a battle art, in which when evoked on a shield it would regenerate durability.  What would be needed to do this and how would it be done?  I look forward to your report.\r\n','2016-10-25 04:56:00'),(10167218,2148010472,2871,436207616,39,'Blaze-Mini 30-Em\'et',0,47,10,-5084,6396,'I want you to help at least three members of the house to get either thier art platted, or a task for the art.  Have Fun. ~Cryst~','2016-10-09 05:55:39'),(12718372,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(12718371,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,26,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:04'),(10118998,4278716900,3070,805306368,39,'Angel of dreams pt2',0,41,11,-6054,-2667,'the touch of her hand lifts me from the mire,\r\nmoving me to a forgotten path\r\ncomfort\r\npeace\r\nhope\r\nthough the path is winding and arduous, she steadies me when I stumble, \r\ncalms me when I grow frightened, guides me when I grow lost\r\nreassurance\r\nserenity\r\nquiet\r\nshe leads me to a place of peace, a place sheltered from my fears, and stands\r\nwatch as I rest.  I know now that she will always be there when I need her\r\ncalm\r\nsleep\r\nlove\r\nThe Angel of my Dreams\r\n','2016-10-03 00:28:33'),(10456969,4127721956,9571326,2751463424,2751018,'Rally Mini - AJ',0,47,11,5327,4423,'Now that we know how Rally works, come up with a way to make a room or a whole plane immune to the art (Just a working theory is fine).\r\n','2016-11-14 01:20:07'),(10127076,17304036,3070,3841982464,39,'Vill\'s Love Poem ?',0,41,11,-6123,-2614,'Lady love, always there, Lady Love, Everywhere, I am here, you are there. I hear your name, \"we are all the same\". ~<3 Vill ~<3','2016-10-04 03:11:29'),(12717640,1459685512,654640141,0,0,'Night Teal Alteror',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10127113,268962276,3070,251658240,43,'~Love~',0,41,11,-6183,-2588,'There is no greater force than love. From ember to brightest star. A drug to so completely ensnare a heart and soul. How else find we light for our path, ease from our burdens, balm for our pain than by love? Love is never unrequited, and returns upon the sending, though we oft see it not. There is no greater hope than love. For love is the only gift we provide to others, but also to ourselves.','2016-10-04 03:28:05'),(10259530,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'FlameShaft | Learn',0,33,22,-99,22834,'Ignite a bit of a fire and pursue a bit of knowledge. First, find out the elements that are related to the focii. Then, learn of the colors of  focus specific talismen that you will generally use as a GateKeeper. Last but not least, learn about the damage values for FlameShaft up to 5th plateau. ','2016-10-21 02:25:11'),(10136600,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'The King - 2',0,41,20,3997,1007,'This distressed the king, instead of interesting him. How could his nothing be something, yet also nothing at the same time? It was a contradiction in nature! It shook the foundation of his world, and because of this, his people suffered. The king began to issue decrees; Nothing will remain nothing, it cannot be something. ','2016-10-05 05:58:25'),(10133968,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'The King - 3',0,41,20,3978,1007,'Because of this, the people of his kingdom began to experience sudden emptinesses in their lives; the nothings in their lives ceased to be somethings, and voids were everpresent allthroughout the land. The king thought he had done the land a great service, but all around him were voids in peoples lives, nothingness so great that it could not be breached. ','2016-10-04 20:58:56'),(10133969,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'The King - 4',0,41,20,3956,1005,'It was not until one clever woman discovered that nothing was something that the kingdom became prosperous again; she visited the king of the land, the king obsessed with nothing, and she bestowed upon him a gift: The Gift of Nothing -- this gift was both something and nothing, and it preyed upon his mind for all time. He became obsessed with the Gift, and troubled his lands no longer. The people of his kingdom went back to the ordinary routes of life, and became quietly prosperous ever after. ','2016-10-04 21:00:49'),(10133935,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'The King - 1',0,41,20,4017,1005,'Once upon a time, there was a king. This king loved nothing more than nothing; he meditated upon the nature of nothing, slept with dreams about nothing, and devoted his time and life to nothing. Until one night, he came to a uncomfortable realization: His nothing, his dear, sweet nothing upon which he devoted all his time, was *something*. ','2016-10-04 20:56:16'),(10221370,526824,2840,922746880,43,'Abjure to 30',0,47,3,3209,1142,'Find ways to aid 5 of your fellow dreamers in their advancement using this art. Think out of the box as much as possible and we\'ll expect a report worthy of this amazing art.','2016-10-16 07:15:09'),(10259595,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Shatter | Learn',0,33,22,50,22834,'Knowing is key. I would like for you to first make a ward and closely examines every detail into how you make it; What is your ward made of? What physical features defines yours from others? FInally, What are some of it\'s strengths and weaknesses. ','2016-10-21 02:32:21'),(12719361,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10205725,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,8793,-4072,'','2016-10-14 02:43:09'),(10205723,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,8233,-1855,'','2016-10-14 02:42:16'),(10210777,285739492,3070,620756992,43,'Undershirt',0,47,5,-3425,3680,'This is a royal undershirt handstitched by the famed seamster Nathan. It is the latest fashion, considered the mark of high class. Evidently, this undergarment is obviously cut to be flattering, and leaves only a minimum to the imagination when worn. Thin and lightweight, this close-cropped undershirt is the preferred style of the Dreamer community.','2016-10-14 19:44:25'),(10164879,1409812964,3345406,637534208,2751019,'Nightmare Form | 30',0,47,11,5327,4416,'-Emphant Adventures with AJ-. I would like for you and 3 friends to evoke nightmare form and I would like for to explore an area uncommonly used. You will be their tour guide, but here\'s the catch: You must give a tour to them of a plane and do so in completely maren. Have fun with this. ','2016-10-08 22:49:53'),(10159110,2198342116,9505790,4261412864,2619433,'CW Mini - Em',0,47,10,-5058,6392,'Chaos hides in the most unlikely of places sometimes.  In rooms, in hidden corners, in peoples packs... Oh no.  That last one could be dangerous.  Those poor, unsuspecting dreamers.  Someone (Say you?) should really save them and make sure they\'re safe.  Help out a couple of people with this and let me know it went.\r\n','2016-10-08 03:47:43'),(10761584,4261939688,2296654,637534208,2699559,'Avayla: Imprison',0,47,5,-2764,3859,'Describe the process by which imprisoning works.','2016-12-20 20:51:31'),(10172583,4127721956,2100222,2751463424,2699562,'Curse - 10',0,47,5,-2798,3865,'Take to the city and see if you can find anything that would be the physical embodiment of curse.  Then when you have that, do an experiment with it (the goal of the experiment or main idea behind it is up to you.) Use help in anyway if you feel needed.  I look forward to hearing what you found and what was done, good luck!\r\n','2016-10-09 22:56:43'),(10168188,67635684,2493438,570425344,2752039,'Trail 10',0,47,5,-3576,2293,'Leave a trail of \"bread crumbs\" as you walk. Be oblivious about it. You may pick your poison as to what you are dropping. How many dreamers start to follow your trails? You can even add a little something for them to find at the very end. Have fun!','2016-10-09 08:36:06'),(10399811,252185064,2843,922746880,43,'Invis to 30',0,47,3,3227,1150,'Invisibility has a sister art in chamele, and vision helps allow one to see through both of them, I want you to expand on the three arts. How can each be better, how can they work in conjunction with each other. Should invis and chamele be merged, if so. How can they be merged effectivly? Is there a better art that could be more battleworthy ? ','2016-11-07 01:22:39'),(10268092,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Shatter | 50',0,33,22,-99,22221,'Mad Ward Scientist. You are one of the most well renknowned GateDoctors in the dream. Perform a few experiments and extend the power of shatter to work on something more interesting. Take your hypothesis and make it a well known theory. \r\n','2016-10-22 05:49:42'),(10226687,4261939684,3070,4261412864,41,'Shadow Summary',0,41,8,272,-8889,'*A heavily worn back book cover* \"In The Shadow of the Mountain, there is no mercy.  6 young dreamers, focused on light hearted exploration are about to find out how true this can be, and how dark the shadows can grow beneath the gaze of the light. \" ','2016-10-16 19:41:40'),(12719360,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10398036,4278716900,3070,2734686208,43,'Finality Prologue',0,41,8,-159,-8883,'There was nothing there, that desert upon which he found himself. The sky above was scorched by the sun, denying all clouds and halting any breeze. Looking past his tattered and sun-bleached clothes he found his worn feet bare, blistered and bleeding. Beneath them the cracked earth seemed to thirstily accept his blood, each drop draining his life away. In the hazy distance he spied the bare remains of a once lush tree - he ran his dry tongue over his parched lips and set out, hoping to find a reason...','2016-11-06 19:55:08'),(10189184,1711802852,3070,1627389952,41,'~ Hiding ~ ',0,41,11,-6857,-2120,'Hiding from my loneliness, but it finds me at every turn, taunting me, laughing, saying.. \"I told you so\".','2016-10-12 01:11:27'),(10319696,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Identify | 10 ',0,33,22,272,22560,'The identity of the talisman. Just like dreamers Talismans are uniquely individual as well. They are born from the marriage of elements and colorations and bear unique individual values. What makes some talismans more than the other? Furthermore, given we all have the ability to achieve the same potential in the dream. Prove to me what gives dreamers value over one another.\r\n','2016-10-28 09:17:02'),(12719359,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719357,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10210841,3121088996,3070,620756992,43,'Ivy engrossed Hat',0,47,5,-3413,3716,'Healthy, green leaves of ivy are wrapped around a the base of the hat. This looks like it would be cool and refreshing against your brow. Such hats of this style are decorated in the standards of its green loving focus. The pattern on this hat are characterized as Berry tierced with Sand: the marks of the SoulMaster.','2016-10-14 19:52:17'),(10205728,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7397,-4366,'','2016-10-14 02:45:58'),(10205727,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,6567,-5305,'','2016-10-14 02:45:49'),(10210840,1141377508,3070,620756992,43,'Focus Robes',0,47,5,-3422,3658,'Heavy and warm,  focal robes typically denote a fervent (and some would say unhealthy) dedication to one focus or another. These robes bear the insignia and coloration of a SoulMaster and will give giggles to dreamers around. Woven from fine harrow jungle textiles, this light robe offers little in the way of protection.','2016-10-14 19:46:33'),(12719356,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719355,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10205730,6037,13437953,0,0,'Red Team',0,43,7,5240,-7277,'','2016-10-14 02:47:48'),(10205722,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7563,-2045,'','2016-10-14 02:42:04'),(10205731,6101,13437953,0,0,'Blue Team',0,43,7,11779,-4665,'','2016-10-14 02:48:39'),(10205679,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7575,-2881,'','2016-10-14 02:35:10'),(10205687,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,10314,-4867,'','2016-10-14 02:36:01'),(10205724,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,9233,-3136,'','2016-10-14 02:42:53'),(10205721,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,7479,-2324,'','2016-10-14 02:41:52'),(10205678,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,6082,-6481,'','2016-10-14 02:35:01'),(10205685,5717,13437953,0,0,'Undergames Crystal',0,43,7,8986,-4484,'','2016-10-14 02:35:48'),(12719354,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10315959,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Shatter | 50',0,33,22,-278,22602,'The power of Intimidation. A variety of dreamers in the dream utilize their combat prowess as a means of oppression. Their backbones are shattered. But, are they truly that much more powerful than the average fifth sphere? Take a moment to analyze combat and raw power differentials. Guage in some political conversations about dreamers who fear these dreamers and attempt to alleviate some tension as well as give them confidence in the abilties they have. ','2016-10-27 20:59:41'),(10284245,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Return | Learn',0,33,22,15,22804,'Time traveling in the dream. Become the master of the time space continuum! Find methods to trace your mistakes and turn back the granite barriers of time. Do not take this task literally, but use your imagination and have fun doing so. ','2016-10-23 23:29:28'),(10242790,4043835880,2873,3338665984,42,'Light of the Moon',0,41,8,67,-8882,'Tall Shadows deep, rich Fire light. Four friends they did travel thru EverNight. But once inside the forest so deep, their fear soon realized, into the moonlight, it did so creep! First one, then two, then three it took! The fourth so frightened, he wildly shook! For in the darkness of Night so bleek, the moors, the meadows, e\'en water does creak!!!! Can he save his friends? Will he make it out... alive???','2016-10-19 00:36:53'),(12719353,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10286674,71289,4110418687,0,0,'Void Crystal',0,17,25,508,-12772,'A crystal which pulsates with a dark light. The crystal seems to drain the energy from anything which it is touched to.','2016-10-24 06:48:03'),(12717638,1375865024,673712129,10,0,'Fire Teal Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717639,1442908296,571147283,0,0,'Cyan Teal Alteror',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10265580,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'GateSmasher | 50',0,33,22,-305,22684,'Take your blading to the next level. Gather a group of dreamers and search the dream for things needed to improve the anatomy of your blade: Adequate metals, forged hammers, wells of water to cool it. Journey to one of the forges and get to work. Refine your blade and improve it so that it is worthy of 5th plateau.  ','2016-10-21 21:44:06'),(10268155,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'GateKeeper | 10',0,33,22,-342,22620,'We all need to take a moment and examine who we are. Go find an area in the dream you like alone and take a moment to listen to enviornment and examine your dreams. What do you want out of the dream? Will you become the greatest warrior in all of the land? Will you become a well respected art creator? The choice is yours!','2016-10-22 05:56:58'),(10259628,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Ward & Amulet | L',0,33,22,26,22804,'Take a journey. Gather your most trusted friend and take a Journey through a plane which you feel is representive of your dreamlife as a GateKeeper. Relate to your focus and Examine any roadblocks, confrontation, highs and lows, and things you\'ve accomplished. Also, learn the basics of Ward and the danger of Amulet.','2016-10-21 02:41:00'),(12717637,906037192,436339224,0,0,'Cyan Gold Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10265517,872942056,2847,637534208,43,'GateSmasher | 30',0,33,22,-103,22794,'Blade creation quests are so cliche in these dreams. Oh boy! I had the same task from three different teachers for three plateaus. Instead of creating a blade....create a shield and armor to guard oneself against the differing blades of the other focuses. Either have some forge a replica or inscribe the schematics. Enjoy yourself!','2016-10-21 21:32:38'),(10268060,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Nightmare Form | 70',0,33,22,316,22499,'Winter Nightmare Form Championship Series. Host a Nightmare Form tournament. Offer a Prize for the winner. Get no less than 10 Participants for 1v1 battles. Make this exciting and fun enough that this will be a continued tradition. This should extend a minimum of three events but no more than 5. Good luck. ','2016-10-22 05:46:26'),(10409552,2047347176,985909,3338665984,2741802,'A Brave New Dream',0,21,16,-2777,-3107,'While the basic layout of the City is as you remember, many things have changed since your last dreams. Speaks with dreamers, old & new, asking for either a tour or directions to new areas. Try to learn about the new arts as well. A journey to the Houses may be a fruitful walk as well. Your experience will be your report. Enjoy! ~Lacie~','2016-11-08 02:35:03'),(10382548,59557,13438207,0,0,'A Spinning Vortex',0,17,32,-1278,8127,'A spinning altar that beams a mystical dark purple beam surrounded by sparkles into the sky seemingly to on for infinity.','2016-11-04 19:43:14'),(10385475,4709,13437953,0,0,'1',0,26,2,261,-3389,'Golden silk dangles from an ornate T-shape pole. The emblem of the Union of the Covenant is embroidered with delicate precision along with a few passages of words underneath. \"Come in peace. Remain in peace. Depart in peace.\"','2016-11-05 05:13:15'),(10284308,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Rally | Learn',0,33,22,-109,22760,'Pep Rally! Show your house/focal spirit. Excite dreamers on an upcoming event or experiment. Show them how to have fun! Play the part and dress up and create a mega phone to proect your dreamer spirit!','2016-10-23 23:37:46'),(10300989,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Reflect | Learn',0,33,22,8,22832,'Shiny Coat. Explore the dream looking for a suitable spring worthy of a magnificent wash. Take this puppy, I want you to polish this puppies coat to the point where you see your reflection in it! I expect nothing less than that! Make his sparkle like a mirror! Additionally, learn the basics of the art. ','2016-10-25 23:43:00'),(10309718,1711802856,1706790,1627389952,2561833,'Time for a change',0,47,9,-4755,3305,'I need a new dress. I get tired of the same old thing. Can you make me one?? now remember! Im not much for showing my aging boobs and stuff!! and I HATE red, fire and gold.. lets see whatcha can come up with for me! *c','2016-10-26 23:43:32'),(10319664,1409812968,2845,637534208,43,'Inscribe | 20',0,33,22,303,22484,'Ancient inscriptions. Among many walls and caves in the dreams lies a variety of ancient inscription. Take a journery throughout the the dream and analyze, ascertain and explicate on these. Upon completion you will take me to these locations and convince me of their meanings.\r\n','2016-10-28 09:09:51'),(10319729,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Newly Awakened | L',0,33,22,294,22533,'Newly Awakened dreamers tend to have a great deal of depth and personality. Most dreamers vastly underate this and fail to see the value in them. For this task, I would like for you to embrace our newly awakened dreamers and actively engage with them. ','2016-10-28 09:26:31'),(10316464,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Reflect | Learn ',0,33,22,-24,22830,'A Poem of Reflection. Write a well versed poem on various reflections. Considering that the Storyteller\'s event is in the next coming days, show off your newly written poem. Your report will be the poem and the reactions. Additionally, learn the basics of Reflect. ','2016-10-27 22:44:56'),(10319352,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'FlameShaft | 30',0,33,22,-258,22536,'Igniting flames in dreamers, houses, and around the dreams are so cliche. I\'d like for you to ask a variety of dreamers and learn about the most repitive/cliche tasks that they have done. Compile a list and inscribe them then bring these tasks to at least 3 teachers. I expect effort worthy of third plateau. ','2016-10-28 08:13:32'),(10316496,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Reflect | 50 ',0,33,22,-262,22692,'The significance of Introspection. Introspection is an analysis of one\'s own mental and emotional processes. It provides privleged access to our own mental states and how they influence our actions. Host a class arguing the necessity of introspection. Also, have dreamers participate in an active introspection session. This class should be worthy of 5th plateau. ','2016-10-27 22:49:36'),(10360828,252185060,3070,2734686208,43,'Ephram\'s Bad Day 1',0,41,13,-3524,-1937,'Ephram the Emphant woke one morning in the Great Dark Beyond, the place where all nightmares begin and end. Today was his day to go stand quietly and motionlessly on the Evernight Plateau, just outside the Sanctuary. \"Damnit all!\" he cursed, knowing it to be the most dangerous job in the dream. \"It must\'ve been when the foreman caught me smoking that chronic during my break the other day...\" he ruminated. Thurman the Bogrom, his foreman, was a strict bastard indeed. Ephram donned his bowler hat...','2016-11-02 02:27:56'),(10385368,53381,13437953,0,0,'Tears',0,26,2,329,-3523,'','2016-11-05 04:55:44'),(10730339,2483554788,3070,637534208,43,'Reweave | Learn',0,47,3,3731,1207,'If there is any underestimated use of equipment in a dreamer\'s arsenal. It would be the shield. This is truly unfortunate given the shield\'s critical role. Given thay you love numbers. Learn the damage values for chakrams of the following levels: 46\'s 50\'s and 60\'s and how much a 10%, 20% and 45% damage reduction shield reduces from these. Also, learn proper maintanence of shields and the best opportunities to utilize this art. ','2016-12-17 07:54:29'),(10339627,526867,317194497,1379093,1537792,'Ward',0,26,28,5209,-3696,'','2016-10-30 18:29:58'),(12717729,1442908296,537199639,0,0,'Cyan Teal Alteror',0,10,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:48'),(10339629,526867,1709703425,1379349,1537792,'Ward',0,26,28,6910,-3695,'','2016-10-30 18:30:36'),(10339631,526867,1172832513,1502743,1537792,'Ward',0,23,32,5778,-1278,'','2016-10-30 18:33:07'),(10339632,526867,4108845313,1502486,1537792,'Ward',0,23,32,4122,-1278,'','2016-10-30 18:33:16'),(10340298,4773,13437953,0,0,'Warning',0,48,5,7600,1150,'WARNING\r\n\r\nThe other side of this portal has been sealed shut.  Those who enter will not be able to leave.  ENTER AT YOUR OWN RISK!','2016-10-30 20:45:19'),(10340685,526867,1860698369,1797403,2620928,'Ward',0,19,34,-7157,-17161,'','2016-10-30 22:11:09'),(10340721,61349,13437953,0,0,'Wish\'s Telescope',0,19,34,-9728,-17329,'A telescope not to dissimilar to the one held at the Alliance.  ','2016-10-30 22:17:02'),(10360393,4127721956,9505790,2751463424,2576938,'Chaos Well - 20',0,47,12,5699,6577,'Come up with a theory to reverse engineer a chaos well.  Technically basically making something that instead of pulling in strength, could somehow eject strength.  What form would the ejection take?  Finally find a creative use that this new well would have on a dreamer!  I look forward to hearing what you come up with, good luck.\r\n','2016-11-02 01:10:00'),(10343063,3876063716,1707006,4160749568,2561831,'Dina - Reweave',0,47,9,-4905,3540,'(Support Task): Go out into the City, and find shields with EVEN 10s in the durabilities! Forged ones don\'t count! You don\'t have to find ALL the 10s, but find at least 3 of them for me! So durabilities 10, 20, 30, 40, 50, 60, etc, etc. But on the even 10s! \r\n','2016-10-31 05:35:14'),(10351128,526820,3070,335544320,43,'Small Wells',0,22,27,-4891,-18234,'Small Wells: These smaller wells are available for filling with essence nodes in case you need them for pure energy purposes.','2016-11-01 01:18:23'),(12719011,100927560,262938,10802,0,'Cyan Chalk Chakram',0,42,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:20'),(10386185,2835876324,1575934,4026531840,2566952,'Recharge -- 70',0,47,11,5925,4157,'With the return of those lost and the defeat of the General, it is past time to recharge the excitement of the City and its citizens. I want you to organize and deligate duties for 3 events that will put the spark back into the CIty around us. I will leave the specifics up to you of course. Use as many people as you need to make this happen. Make your efforts worthy of a plateau of this level. **A**','2016-11-05 07:34:14'),(12719352,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719351,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719350,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719349,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10350769,526820,3148798,4261412864,2752039,'Push',0,47,5,-3603,2287,'Hic-ups are annoying.  But what about running into a room - screaming \"Boolia boolia! Ha!!\" and pushing someone... and running off.  The only way to stop you from running off and doing this.  Is to be Pushed back.   Continue this festering disease until a cure is found!  But mostly.... have fun.  ','2016-11-01 00:12:24'),(12719348,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(12719330,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,50,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:28'),(12719329,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,50,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:28'),(12719328,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,50,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:28'),(10362917,671615460,3070,2281701376,40,'Top Gens 3rd sphere',0,41,10,-2440,-9314,'There are many, the top ones I found for 3rd sphere are as follows:  Teng\'s Treasure Hoard, LC with Sham.  There are three in Caudal Rift, Fayd\'s Betrayal gen is 4th step from top with ago, NW inner ring have to jump to small beam to reach gen with ago, Horron\'s Lair with two invisable gens inbetween the four spikes with a Horron.  Harrow Glades has two North/South Outer Circle both with Shams.  Two in Chasm of Souls, The Spiked Crossing and The Rings of Woe both with Shams.','2016-11-02 09:03:35'),(10360860,252185060,3070,2734686208,43,'Ephram\'s Bad Day 2',0,41,13,-3515,-1926,'... hung his briefcase from his center back-horn, and headed out to the Dream-Beam; the portal to the dream, and to the Evernight Plateau on this particular day. Thurman laughed at Ephram as he floated on to the portal platform, and wickedly wished him, \"Good luck, hah!\" Ephram maintained his composure, shut his eyes, breathed in deeply, and waited for the woosh. Moments passed, and nothing. Ephram opened his eyes slowly to look around, and discovered Thurman was gone. \"Strange,\" he thought...','2016-11-02 02:31:23'),(10385546,526867,1474822401,129793,2615296,'Ward',0,26,2,954,-4253,'','2016-11-05 05:20:49'),(10362952,671615460,3070,2281701376,40,'Top Gens 3rd spher2',0,41,10,-2409,-9315,'There are two in Dorsal Rift.  Temple of Insanity which the gen is in the dark pit in the middle with a horron, and Shrine of Horron which you have to jump on a small beam to reach the gen and no mare in the room.  Gloom Peaks has three gens:  Hershal\'s Fallen Way gen is on the path road at the end with an ago, Blood hall and The blood baths both have shams.  There is one decent gen in Albino Caves, Vile Retreat with a Sham.  There is also one in Ossuaray of Dread in the Darkened Passage with an ago.','2016-11-02 09:14:22'),(10367783,55973,13437953,0,0,'1',0,48,5,9048,-135,'The flame pulsates almost as if it is breathing.  If you look closely, shapes and forms can be see forming inside the flame before quickly dissipating.','2016-11-03 01:08:36'),(10368408,315305,486540033,10301,0,'Mace of Castigation',0,48,6,19952,996,'Five blades form the head of the enormous Mace of Castigation.  The mace appear bound, unable to be lifted.  The blades surround a large orb.  Several glowing spheres orbit around inside of the orb.','2016-11-03 03:00:26'),(12717728,1610680264,335544852,0,0,'Chalk Cyan Elemen',0,10,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:48'),(10761851,34081252,2558974,1191182336,2699560,'Scare10-Avayla',0,47,5,-2732,3864,'I would like for you to have a scare duel. Have someone scare you and someone else at random times while dueling. How much did this effect the outcome? Did it give an underdog an edge? Did you become more comfortable as the duel went on with being scared and discover how you may control it? Have a few of these duels and report to me your findings, did you get better or was there just no use in trying to go against it? We will discuss!','2016-12-20 21:44:09'),(10374805,59557,13438207,0,0,'Vortex Generator',0,21,31,5144,-264,'A spinning altar that beams a mystical dark purple beam surrounded by sparkles into the sky seeming to go on for infinity.','2016-11-03 23:58:40'),(10375843,688392680,9571129,4194304000,2576937,'Rally ~ mini',0,47,12,5627,6582,'Devise a rallying cry to yell for when you evoke this art! See if you can use it in practice.','2016-11-04 03:32:02'),(10385408,64037,13437953,0,0,'Archon\'s Shield',0,26,2,256,-3020,'A worn shield with mutliple fractures and dents. The emblem of the Union of the Covenant is visible although nearly faded. The motto \"One Voice, One Heart, One Union\" is engraved around the edges.','2016-11-05 05:03:35'),(10385231,63205,13437953,0,0,'Pristine Stone',0,26,2,257,-3311,'An ornate marble tombstone with the following words engraved onto it surface. \"In Memory of Matron\"','2016-11-05 04:42:48'),(10382263,59557,13438207,0,0,'A Spinning Vortex',0,18,32,335,11087,'A spinning altar that beams a mystical dark purple beam surrounded by sparkles into the sky seemingly to on for infinity.','2016-11-04 18:44:23'),(10678794,1409812968,2860,637534208,43,'Chaos Well | Learn',0,47,3,3613,1215,'Chaos deals with complex systems of energy whose behavior is highly sensitive to slight changes in conditions, so that small alterations can give rise to strikingly great consequences. Fayd\'s Fortress is a prime example of this type of situation. Engage in conversations with dreamers and learn of 3 negative occurances. Additionally, learn what essences can and can\'t be placed inside the wells and how plateauing effect this art.','2016-12-11 00:55:42'),(10385513,526867,4209508609,133121,2615296,'Ward',0,26,2,-467,-4287,'','2016-11-05 05:20:39'),(10382264,59557,13438207,0,0,'A Spinning Vortex',0,22,31,-4006,1810,'A spinning altar that beams a mystical dark purple beam surrounded by sparkles into the sky seemingly to on for infinity.','2016-11-04 18:46:15'),(10386218,2835876324,4000766,4026531840,2752040,'Sphere pre-task',0,47,5,-3628,2247,'For this portion of your training, you are to raise your train level to 20 and work on gaining another train task to 30. Also speak with as many Master Teachers and other Teachers who have the ability to sphere. Learn all that you can and come up with ideas of what you think sphere tasks should include. Return when you are ready and we will continue your training. **A**','2016-11-05 07:41:40'),(10385547,526867,3085435137,110081,2615296,'Ward',0,26,2,1160,-3374,'','2016-11-05 05:20:57'),(10385370,53381,13437953,0,0,'Tears',0,26,2,259,-3521,'','2016-11-05 04:58:43'),(10399739,252185064,2843,922746880,43,'Invis to learn',0,47,3,3275,1142,'There are many hidden doorways and within our City.  I would like you to seek some of them out and also give me your personal theory as to  why they are hidden. In addition to these I\'d like the basics surrounding this art.. cost, orbit etcetera. I look forward to hearing your report.','2016-11-07 01:15:03'),(10399778,252185064,2843,922746880,43,'Invis to 10 ',0,47,3,3262,1149,'I want you to do a poll, I want you to develop 4 questions about the art of invisibility, questions that you may have yourself,  or ones you think are important to a better understanding of the art.  I want you to ask at least 10 others your questions. Record their answers and responses. I look forward to hearing your report.','2016-11-07 01:19:00'),(10461993,252185060,3070,2734686208,43,'Ephram\'s Bad Day 4',0,41,13,-3517,-1909,'Horace stopped cold in his tracks, remaining silent and fixated on Ephram, who in turn was frozen to the spot above the Dream-Beam. It seemed like hours passed, and Ephram soiled himself slightly, as the desire to urinate becoming overwhelming. Finally, Horace spoke, \"Dude! Woah, don\'t harsh my buzz!\" Ephram looked up from his tremulous wings, feeling quite confused. Horace finally asked, \"Bro, I heard you had some reefer? Wanna hit my office, hot box the place, and mellow out on some ludes?\" - The End','2016-11-14 16:54:36'),(10456777,285739492,3070,3841982464,39,'a Bright Red Rose',0,20,19,15951,-12245,'In Memory Of Heaven Alexis','2016-11-14 00:45:15'),(10409873,688392680,2872,4194304000,41,'AJ\'s',0,41,8,433,-8885,'Arlyana Jax\'s entry into the cover contest','2016-11-08 03:35:24'),(12717614,1124141192,654574616,0,0,'Gold Jade Alteror',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(10461992,252185060,3070,2734686208,43,'Ephram\'s Bad Day 3',0,41,13,-3521,-1918,'... looking for his foreman - a bogrom who had never left his post, and never failed to exact vengeance on those that displeased him. Suddenly, from the shadows was thrown the desiccated corpse of the foreman, which crumpled in a pile at his tail. What emerged from the shadows thereafter sent a chill down Ephram\'s back-horns - it was the big boss! It was Horace, the horron. Horace\'s fiery pinpoint gaze fixed itself on Ephram, and he froze with dread. \"I\'d rather a dreamer collapse me, sir! BE MERCIFUL!\"','2016-11-14 16:53:39'),(10523556,526867,3068657921,181250,1538816,'Ward',0,23,3,26,-5984,'','2016-11-22 03:01:10'),(10442454,4144499172,9636862,1392508928,2699559,'Channel',0,47,5,-2703,3862,'Waste not, want not is how the saying goes. Well this delicious art solves that problem. Channel is a beautiful new art that helps everyone. Find out what you can about the art and then tell me what you think about it. Any insights you have on how you will  use it? Or you could write a quick little peom aobut how it came to be or something like that. Have fun. It\'s a quest, not a task. Jokes for days!! <T>','2016-11-12 09:03:51'),(12717613,3271624648,704709143,0,0,'Gold Beige Elemen',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(10446850,2131233252,3070,721420288,39,'Combine 1/2',0,3,29,-11340,4479,'Ibioc was a great Master that worked diligently on Recharge.His knowledge of talisman was unrivalled. Like many of the Great Smiths, he too studied at one time under the Srechethan Kabal. The art of combine was already old when Ibioc discovered Recharge. He knew how natural and easy Combine is compared to Recharge in many respects. Ibioc wanted to do more than just fuse talisman together...He sought to dig deeper into an item & increase its power. His oath to the Guild prevented him from revealing Combine.','2016-11-12 22:39:42'),(10446855,1862797796,3070,721420288,39,'Combine History 2/2',0,41,5,-264,-6971,'But he took no oath on his own discoveries, so Combine was kept a secret. The decision to bring this art back to the Guild and to break his silence was prompted by Falinor\'s ordeal with  Iden\'s betrayal of Falinor within the Ambiance and the tampering he did  there was his guide. The 1st 3 non-elder dreamers to be granted this Art at the same time were LovesIight, Munchkin and tux. Combine was a art for Master Seers that were in the Guild.','2016-11-12 22:43:24'),(10446853,2131233252,3070,721420288,39,'Combine 2/2',0,3,29,-11331,4454,'But he took no oath on his own discoveries, so Combine was kept a secret. The decision to bring this art back to the Guild and to break his silence was prompted by Falinor\'s ordeal with  Iden\'s betrayal of Falinor within the Ambiance and the tampering he did  there was his guide. The 1st 3 non-elder dreamers to be granted this Art at the same time were LovesIight, Munchkin and tux. Combine was a art for Master Seers that were in the Guild.','2016-11-12 22:41:37'),(10508704,4144499176,1444675,419430400,2751015,'Blend-60',0,47,11,5327,4419,'The altars at the facades are intriguing. They seem to allow the Dark Mares to walk to our facades as easily as a portal. Would this work for us? Organize a plan to use an Altar to either teleport to the Dark Awakening OR to one of the other House Planes they reside on. Execute your plan. Did it work? Did you blow up? Try not to lose your soul essence in the attempt.','2016-11-20 05:49:19'),(10456200,117481,471074047,0,0,'Helix Torch',0,22,2,762,-3974,'A torch, shining brightly as it emits a ray of light upward into the sky above. The light a constant, an unwavering beam that glows brilliantly for all to see.','2016-11-13 22:29:42'),(10454688,2668104168,2852,1023410176,43,'Inz - Rally Mini',0,47,11,5327,4424,'RAH RAH RAH! Lift their spirits! Rally 3 dreamers with cheerful words of encouragement! Bring out the cheer leader in you and come up with some exciting ways to morally support your fellows on their missions or projects.','2016-11-13 17:50:28'),(10523557,526867,501743873,163330,1538816,'Ward',0,23,3,518,-6364,'','2016-11-22 03:01:15'),(12717636,654379144,654443538,0,0,'Night Fire Alteror',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717635,2298546120,738394647,0,0,'Plum Azure Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10555107,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Identify | 50',0,33,22,-41,22193,'In order to improve the outcome of our efforts, we must heed to some constructive criticism in our lives. This process of offering valid and well-reasoned opinions about the work of others should involve both positive and negative comments.  This should be in a friendly manner rather than an oppositional one.  Interview the rulers of the dream and identify general areas of improvement. After this is complete, hold a gathering on improving leadership. Ensure this is thoroughly done. ','2016-11-25 20:50:47'),(10523560,526867,4192731393,388357,1538816,'Ward',0,23,6,-2267,-5388,'','2016-11-22 03:01:38'),(12717634,838994112,421070849,10,0,'Fire Gold Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10483045,2835876324,2362366,4026531840,2752040,'Trap Nightmare 50',0,47,5,-3572,2255,'Most of the citizens are trapped in a constant cycle. They gain arts and spheres and then work on something else. The City grows in number and then it levels off. Find examples of  at least five examples of dreamers that are trapped in their own cycle and how you would suggest assisting them break that cycle. Make your efforts worthy of the plateau that you seek. **A**','2016-11-17 05:00:51'),(10547135,2936539624,2833,2231369728,39,'~Darkness~',0,41,10,-2326,-9433,'Everyone knows this art.  Mass darkness, easily defeated by vision.  So whats the point of the art then? Simple, use it when they least expect it.  As a defender it has limited uses. Since your enemy generally comes prepared.  However, if YOU choose the time and place to attack you enemies (be it gen time, diner time, house meeting time), you can sneak onto their plane and cast it throwing the enemy into confusion if they arent ready, giving your side the advantage of attacking an unprepared target!','2016-11-25 00:27:07'),(10713696,1325402917,13437953,0,0,'Black Rose',0,26,2,282,-3286,'A black rose in full bloom. The petals are soft to the touch. The stem is bereft of thorns. ','2016-12-15 06:48:01'),(10513353,2047347176,2883,3338665984,42,'Low Res Ele\'s',0,21,16,-2808,-3055,'I know...lame! But useful to use for Sacrifice! Please leave here, or use if you need them. Please don\'t toss. ~Lacie~','2016-11-20 19:50:58'),(12576215,1392576648,621085707,0,0,'Gold Teal Alteror',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-07 17:43:59'),(12719347,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10523561,526867,1458045185,414982,1538816,'Ward',0,23,6,-1788,-6551,'','2016-11-22 03:01:50'),(12718889,1208223752,67175187,10752,0,'Azure Jade Charm',0,39,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:17'),(12718888,2835417032,553845272,0,0,'Plum Berry Elemen',0,39,18,-11248,1504,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:17'),(10692182,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Judgement | L',0,47,3,3692,1149,'Given that you are still uninitiated. Explain to me why you choose to spend your dreams unaffiliated with the current houses. Then map out a plan to garner dreamers to follow a house under your leadership. Choose a plane to place your own stronghold on and tell me why.  Also, tell me the basics of Judgement and proper etiquette in regards to this art. ','2016-12-12 20:02:57'),(10533027,3876063716,6163454,4160749568,2751015,'Arlyana - Sacrif 20',0,47,11,5327,4418,'Write ME a poem upon the nature of Sacrifice. Hold the poem to a form of your choice, but ensure that it has a form. Even one of your invention works, but make it a GOOD one if you invent the form! ','2016-11-23 01:50:54'),(12717633,3321956296,704774671,0,0,'Cyan Beige Elemen',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10533061,1913129448,1313634,1493172224,2751019,'Jax Sight!',0,47,11,5327,4414,'Pick a plane. Learn as much as you possibly can about this plane\'s history! Then forge up some glasses that allow others to see this history first hand and take them on a tour of the past! Make this as engrossing as possible!','2016-11-23 02:03:21'),(10678889,1409812968,2864,637534208,43,'Channel | Learn',0,47,3,3671,1148,'Channeling effort is an important skill to have when trying to make progression. Time efficiency is a skill many dreamers lack in the current dreams. Take this Chaos Well and fill it up. Take an Inscription of every single bit of energy you place into it. Return to me with the note and full well and how you filled it. We will discuss this upon completion. Additionally, tell me this art\'s mechanics. Good luck!','2016-12-11 01:09:06'),(12719346,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,51,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:29'),(10538434,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Kinesis | 30',0,33,22,15,22169,'Constructive Motivation. Motivation of others is a major function of effective leadership. There are bad types of motivation and good, the former using fear, intimidation, and the latter using effective delegaion. Motivate members of your home into experimentation on the altars, the node of at GotE, or planning out methodation to take down Xun\'rok. Vocalize your concerns against apathy and make noticeable differences. ','2016-11-23 20:04:55'),(10735371,3876063720,2875,4160749568,39,'Bounties Unpaid:',0,47,10,-5135,6380,'\r\nCalabosh: 30k\r\nNathan: 10k','2016-12-18 01:12:32'),(10762888,4027058660,3070,620756992,43,'Important Essence',0,21,27,6504,-18705,'Do not dspose. Leave right here! This is not my essence. ','2016-12-21 00:57:50'),(10549242,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Drain Essence | 20',0,33,22,-158,22211,'Did you know that Sacrifice and Corrupt -imprisons- essences? In lyra days, having these arts would surely tantaumount suicide! Approach some of the more conservative individuals of the dream and educate them on the mediums of which we deal with essences. WARNING: Be sure to keep your arts up! This task may ensue violent behavior! Additionally, explicate on how conflicting beliefs dilude leadership. ','2016-11-25 07:19:50'),(10549049,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Meditation | 50',0,33,22,-165,22230,'Meditation is often an underated and powerful tool at a leader\'s disposal. Meditation actually builds resilience through decreased  anxiety, thereby potentially boosting resilience and performance under stress. As of lately, some of our leaders in this dream have become apathetic, restless, and irritatble. First consider why this is and follow up on some theruputic methodation. Speak to these dreamers and ask them about their happiest experiences and attempt to help them relax using these situations.','2016-11-25 06:40:07'),(10549403,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'FireStorm | 70',0,33,22,-125,22222,'Charisma is a fire, a fire that ignites followers’ energy and commitment, producing results above and beyond the call of duty. Charisma resides in the relationship between a leader who has charisma and those of his or her followers who are open to charisma, within a charisma-conducive environment. Over the next few weeks ignite dreamers into taking down Xun\'rok, and establishing our dominance. Create a firestorm of our unified passion to protect our city. Make sure this is worthy of 7th plateau. ','2016-11-25 07:46:04'),(10549531,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Trail | 20',0,33,22,16,22168,'Throughout the dream are many symbols as well as interprative artistic endeavors. Dreamers of the past used art as a means of communicating many messages to us. FInd art throughout the dream and prepare a tour with a centralized theme. After you are finished express  to me how this tour taught you to lead. ','2016-11-25 08:03:46'),(10764128,526867,1709703425,1285139,1537792,'Ward',0,46,21,-1665,-2671,'','2016-12-21 04:56:35'),(10766231,302516712,2820,922746880,43,'recharged',0,22,18,6772,-16553,'1 blew up on me and another drained while under 10 charges, making it blow up as well. I i threw in 2 that i had that are equivalent. Enjoy !','2016-12-21 11:48:54'),(10555188,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Reweave | Learn',0,33,22,44,22201,'Reweave some of the dreamers in their social circles. Make some attempts to hang out with a different crowd and see the dream from a different perspective. Lead some efforts into tying dreamers of different backgrounds to dream togther. Additionally, tell me the basics for the art. Have fun!','2016-11-25 21:02:25'),(10755335,526867,3722969345,124417,1537792,'Ward',0,24,2,1140,-2319,'','2016-12-20 00:49:44'),(10571003,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'DreamQuake | Learn',0,33,22,-179,22221,'The earthquake is a powerful symbol. It represents the anxious emotions that stirs inside one while the shaking is happening. It truly means that a major force is threatening our stability and foundation of dreaming. Create a device(literal or figurative) that will give us stability  and positive assurance of our safeties. Additionally, learn the duration for the art up to 5th plateau. ','2016-11-27 21:53:55'),(10702998,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Blind | Learn',0,47,3,3653,1215,'Muscle memory is a powerful utility that some our older dreamers have. It consolidates specific motor tasks into memory through repetition. When a movement is repeated over time, a long term muscle memory is created for that task. Have someone blind you, and attempt to traverse a commonly used room by muscle memory. Your report will be an example. As per requirements, learn the basics of this art. Good luck.','2016-12-14 02:10:40'),(12717632,268568768,286328833,3,0,'Chalk Blood Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717631,151259208,131886,10767,0,'Plum Chalk Chakram',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(12717630,838994112,437913601,10,0,'Fire Gold Shield',0,8,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:46'),(10588207,3876063716,3070,4160749568,39,'Datoken Essences',0,21,16,-2544,-3426,'Place your Datoken Essences here to collect Bounty; then post to me on the boards. 10k xp per essence. ','2016-11-29 20:11:10'),(10679806,3876063716,9571326,4160749568,2803495,'Lace - Rally',0,47,11,5690,4310,'(Support task): Rally someone back in time -- to HISTORY! Rally someone to a place they otherwise could not reach, and teach them about a piece of history you witnessed, or know that occured there. Try to select someone who\'s at least mildly interested! \r\n','2016-12-11 04:11:47'),(12717612,1879115720,385876496,0,0,'Chalk Night Elemen',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717611,537004224,320014337,2,0,'Chalk Fire Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717610,537004224,387385345,4,0,'Chalk Fire Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717609,1124141192,621020172,0,0,'Gold Jade Alteror',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717608,335808520,16843549,10752,0,'Jade Blood Charm',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(10607444,4144499176,9636672,419430400,2564647,'Channel-Learn',0,47,12,5076,6416,'Prepare yourself for being able to Channel your Strength to another. Give something of yours (your time, your energy, your expertise, etc...) to another Dreamer in need. Return with the details, preferably nothing explicit.','2016-12-02 03:59:46'),(10631944,4027058660,3070,620756992,43,'For Em\'et',0,47,11,5999,4544,'Here are two Raichuelle essences and two Tihai essences for you. This is for Em\'et. Do not touch!','2016-12-05 07:40:50'),(10630928,135473,1667434497,99,0,'Srechethan Flag',0,21,30,11323,-12131,'\"We are the Srechethan\" is inscribed beneath the symbol on the banner.','2016-12-05 04:05:17'),(10606238,252185060,3070,2013265920,39,'Soul Shield',0,41,11,-6430,-2571,'Soul shield has many practical uses that may escape common knowledge. The first and most logical use is to evoke it agressively, preventing another dreamer from mindblanking. You could also use it to stop others from removing your own mindblank. A dreamer might also utilize it as an extra defense against abjure. So be aware, soul shield is a very functional art!','2016-12-01 23:45:39'),(10615028,4144499176,4918081,419430400,2752039,'MindBlank-30',0,47,5,-3604,2326,'Soul Shield currently blocks Mind Blank. What makes Mind Blank special? How does Soul Shield recognize that it\'s Mind Blank? Attempt to use that knowledge as the basis for your next experiment.','2016-12-03 05:52:42'),(10619106,526867,736624897,9216,1537792,'Ward',0,24,1,-527,-1525,'','2016-12-03 20:03:07'),(10619110,4485,13437953,0,0,'KoES Flag',0,24,1,1175,-328,'','2016-12-03 20:04:48'),(10619109,4485,13437953,0,0,'KoES Flag',0,24,1,-594,-297,'','2016-12-03 20:04:28'),(10619071,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,23,2052,-11633,'','2016-12-03 19:52:30'),(12576204,16910528,185272321,6,0,'Blood Chalk Shield',0,6,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-07 17:43:58'),(10620500,2131233252,3070,3456106496,42,'Recharge Please',0,17,19,16484,373,'Items needing recharge pretty please and thank you!                        ~Snow Angel~','2016-12-04 00:27:27'),(10619105,526867,3253207297,47104,1537792,'Ward',0,24,1,296,-1525,'','2016-12-03 20:02:35'),(10619104,526867,2129133825,9472,1537792,'Ward',0,24,1,1124,-1525,'','2016-12-03 20:02:28'),(10745153,4144499176,9636676,419430400,2579751,'Channel-Learn',0,18,31,16567,-6266,'Channel is about giving and receiving. Channel your energies into completing a task for yourself and then help someone else with one of their own as well. Do you feel accomplished?','2016-12-18 22:02:20'),(10692119,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Identify | Learn',0,47,3,3758,1201,'Identify that dreamer. Have one dreamer play a game of dreamer identification. Rules are simple: you may not say their name nor alter your appearance. You must spend imitate speech patterns and actions. Do this for 4 dreamers. Additionally, learn what information is learned upon successful evokation of this art. ','2016-12-12 19:46:34'),(10639146,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,30,-5500,-1505,'','2016-12-06 07:03:15'),(10639148,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,23,2060,-11004,'','2016-12-06 07:03:28'),(10632575,4278716900,2100222,385875968,2752039,'Curse 30',0,47,5,-3634,2323,'Currently, curse sees a lot of usage on oneself for imping arts, but we aren\'t actually able to do so. Assuming this was intentional on the part of its creators, support thoughts on why it holds this restriction. - Frey','2016-12-05 09:40:21'),(12576202,318834824,604046355,0,0,'Gold Blood Alteror',0,6,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-07 17:43:58'),(10639145,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,23,3265,-10998,'','2016-12-06 07:03:08'),(10638613,526867,2666004737,366085,1538816,'Ward',0,23,5,1783,-12949,'','2016-12-06 05:17:24'),(10639147,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,23,3250,-11637,'','2016-12-06 07:03:22'),(10692021,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Invisibility | L',0,47,3,3626,1215,'As a DreamSeer, you will come to find that Invisibility is nearly useless in most cases. Dreamers and Nightmares alike can sense your presence regardless of your efforts to cloak yourself. To make manners worse, almost everyone can heighten their senses and negate this art entirely. DreamWright masters sought to create opportunities for Dreamers to become invisible regardless. Explore the dream and discover some areas where you are imperceptible by any means. Also, tell me the basics of the art. ','2016-12-12 19:22:13'),(10835133,302516712,5704505,2734686208,2803499,'Purp CorEss 10 mini',0,47,11,5689,4308,'Corrupt Essence is only really useful if you spend every moment you have to collapse dreamers and \"farm\" their essences. Design me a theoretical NEW Corrupt Essence art, one that would be more useful. Consider one way the new art could be used aggressively, and one way it could be used peacefully.','2016-12-30 01:28:37'),(10669483,2835876324,1575934,4026531840,2803496,'Recharge -- 70',0,47,11,5689,4306,'I wish for you to reflect on five things from your past or present that you wish had gone another way. Now it is time to plan and adjust your past. When you have isolated your issues, make ways that, if you were able to change, would have ensured success. Recharge the mistakes of the past and present to shape a new future. Be prepared to discuss what those future changes might be and if they would be acceptable. **A**','2016-12-10 01:20:56'),(10725517,302516712,2875,2734686208,43,'The Two Wishes Pt2',0,47,10,-4802,5762,'\"A hamburger, fries and an ale.\" The ostrich said, \"I\'ll have the same.\" Again the man reached into his pocket and paid with the exact number. It became routine until one day when they entered, \"The usual?\" asked the waitress. \"No, this is Friday night, so I will have a steak, baked potato and a salad,\" said the man. \"Same,\" said the ostrich. Shortly the waitress brought the order and said, \"That will be 326 essences.\" Once again the man pulled the exact number from his pocket and placed them on the table.','2016-12-16 17:03:19'),(10755298,526867,4075290881,131073,1537792,'Ward',0,24,2,-370,-4159,'','2016-12-20 00:44:11'),(10788763,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 10',0,47,3,3716,1081,'Dreamers are skeptical of one another due to their associations. Generally speaking, the dreamer\'s communitiy are divided into two groups: \"Peace Corpse\" vs. \"all else. With an exception being a few neutral stance dreamers who delve between both groups of dreamers without issue. Ask a dreamer from one of these neutral dreamer to get information of choice from the other. Then, eavesdrop on the conversation by sitting silently in the room. Report to me the effectiveness of this strategy and your experience. ','2016-12-24 08:02:01'),(10685161,34081252,9571326,1191182336,2564648,'RallyL-Jade',0,47,12,5076,6564,'Find a few ways rally has been used to save some time or get someone out of a bind. Return to me with the stories of how rally has already impacted and improved our dreaming and some really original uses!\r\n','2016-12-11 21:33:36'),(12719327,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,50,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:28'),(10691952,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Misdirection | L',0,47,3,3660,1148,'Deception is a trick or scheme used to get what you want. Engage in a few conversations on matters of dire importance at a few dreamer\'s most inconvenient time (During hunting, tasking, etc). Take note of your victim\'s reaction and asses if they sucker into the distraction. Additionally, tell me some good opportunities to utilize this art and the basic mechanics. ','2016-12-12 19:11:44'),(10693866,1997015524,3070,1342177280,40,'Recharging Corner',0,22,18,6601,-16559,'Place things you would like recharged here. Frey and I both have a 50 recharge, so there are chances for explosions! \r\n*Disclaimer* We are not held accountable for blow ups!\r\n***Things recharged will be placed on the opposite side of here.','2016-12-13 01:43:13'),(10692055,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Vision | Learn',0,47,3,3682,1148,'Step away from your reflection in the Lambent Waterfall for a few dreams and stop looking in the mirror. In doing so, you\'ll realize the only one so concerned and critical of your appearance is yourself. Utilize Inscribe or Forge and paint a portrait of a \"successful you\" in the future. Visualize changes necessary to your success, for a change, rather than your superficial qualities. On the other hand, learn the duration of the art up to 5th plateau. ','2016-12-12 19:36:47'),(10725519,302516712,2874,2734686208,43,'The Two Wishes Pt4',0,47,10,-4776,5772,'\"That\'s brilliant!\" said the waitress, \"Most people would ask for a million essences or something, but you\'ll always be as rich as you want for as long as you live!\" - \"That\'s right. Whether it\'s a pint of ale or an entire armory full of abyss shields, the exact payment is always there,\" said the man. The waitress asked, \"So what\'s with the ostrich?\" The man sighed, paused and answered, \"My second wish was for a tall chick with long legs who agrees with everything I say.\" ','2016-12-16 17:04:04'),(10691920,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Rally | Learn',0,47,3,3744,1201,'Over and over again, our city is held at the mercy from dreamers of another city. They consistently display superior in and out of the art of battle. It is time we rally dreamers to prepare themselves for battle. Devise a battle tactic and test it on one dreamer. Challenge them to a real duel and use this knowledge to further your own efforts. Additionally, learn about how this art works. ','2016-12-12 19:07:58'),(10694833,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Scare | Learn',0,47,3,3748,1148,'Haiku of Fright. Write a 3 line Haiku on the art of scare. The caveat is writing one with a surprise ending. Write two lines about something scary in the dream. Then write a third line that is a complete surprise from the first. Does the combination of these two seemingly unrelated parts suggest any surprising relationships? Does it give you any interesting ideas? Ensure a thoroughly developed Haiku. Also, tell me the duration of the scare effect up to 3rd plateau. Have fun.','2016-12-13 04:56:29'),(10795911,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Know | 30',0,47,3,3430,1086,'Know has undergone a drastic overhaul. Some of our former scryers of dreams past have combined their knowledge of insight and scrying into the once nearly useless art. How does the new know offer personal guidance? Is there prophecy or revelation in this newly improved art? If so, evoke it once and tell me what the medium has told you. Additionally, share this knowledge with 10 dreamers. Ensure a thorough report.','2016-12-25 06:36:57'),(10701067,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Stagger | Learn',0,47,3,3734,1148,'First, have a FateSender create a stagger charm for you. Then play a little game. Collect a selection of musical sounds from arts (Random, Meditation, Recharge, Curse, Purify etc) and demonstrate the combination of arts in a pattern of choice. If they guess correctly, then give them a reward. If they fail, use the charm and make them dance! Also learn the duration of stagger up to 5th plateau. Be sure to get permission first! Have fun!','2016-12-13 19:22:38'),(10702744,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Firestorm | Learn',0,47,3,3784,1200,'Firestorm is one of the most powerful FateSender\'s arts. Fire as a symbol, varies among different cultures but is universally linked to destruction and fear. Express your mastery over luciditc fire in a symbolic dance representing flame. Use chakrams, flames, and other symbolic representations of Flame in your dance routine. Additionally, learn the basics of this art. Good luck. ','2016-12-14 01:27:34'),(12576194,3422619592,872677913,0,0,'Beige Elemen',0,6,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-07 17:43:58'),(10709054,285739496,4787002,3087007744,2566953,'Lucky #7',0,47,11,5923,4158,'For your 70 plateau I would like you to write 7 notes to 7 different dreamers. Within, tell them something that yo admire about them, and then something that you hope to see them overcome. ++SC++','2016-12-14 21:54:30'),(10753347,60613,13437953,0,0,'Lightning',0,39,25,-457,-2769,'','2016-12-19 18:36:09'),(10717710,856164840,4786988,687865856,2566951,'inscribe mini 70',0,47,11,5921,4158,'lets get festive!. with your inscribe, decorate at least 5 rooms for the up comming holiday, each room needs to be decked out in full gala, decorated tree\'s, yule stuff, presants under the tree ect ect. if you like you could also start a snowball fight. a pass it along one of course:) have fun with it','2016-12-15 20:29:12'),(12717607,318834632,234947091,0,0,'Gold Blood Elemen',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717606,822216896,471599105,5,0,'Blood Gold Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(12717605,805439680,454756353,3,0,'Chalk Gold Shield',0,7,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:45'),(10736095,3876063720,2874,4160749568,39,'Supports',0,47,10,-5328,6160,'\r\nSense Dreamers - Aileron, Arlyana Jax, Arnaya, LadySilver\r\nRandom - Aileron, Cianne, Myridian Sun, Golah\r\nDeafen - Dreiko, Flower of Cienn, Inzoum, Cianne, Golah\r\nRadiant Blaze - Purple Lace(?)\r\nStagger - Sorsha, Myridian Sun, Flower of Cienn\r\nChannel - LadySilver(?)','2016-12-18 03:34:16'),(10755299,526867,988283137,1499415,1537792,'Ward',0,24,30,-3502,-1697,'','2016-12-20 00:44:44'),(10730244,2483554788,3070,637534208,43,'Poison | Learn',0,47,3,3636,1151,'Have you ever tried to catch someone stealthily by surprise, only to have them turn around and ask why you\'re making so much noise? Well, that has to stop! As a SoulMaster, you will often find yourself the center of the attention due to the nature and danger of your arts (Abjure/Poison). Take this Poison imbued dagger and successfully poison someone without notice. Examine your surroundings and strike when you can. Also, learn the basics of the art. Good luck. ','2016-12-17 07:41:40'),(10725518,302516712,2875,2734686208,43,'The Two Wishes Pt3',0,47,10,-4787,5769,'The waitress could not hold back her curiosity any longer, \"Excuse me, sir. How do you manage to always come up with the exact change in your pocket every time?\" - \"Well,\" said the man, \"several years ago I was wandering around Caudal Rift and found an old lamp lying in the corner. When I rubbed it, a genie appeared and offered me two wishes. My first wish was that if I ever had to pay for anything, I would just put my hand in my pocket and the right amount of essences would always be there.\"','2016-12-16 17:03:43'),(10725516,302516712,2875,2734686208,43,'The Two Wishes Pt1',0,47,10,-4820,5767,'A man walked into a the Chak & Flask with a full-grown ostrich behind him. The waitress asked them for their orders. The man said, \"A hamburger, fries and an ale.\" She turned to the ostrich. \"What\'s yours?\" she asked the ostrich. \"I\'ll have the same,\" said the ostrich. A short time later the waitress returned with the order. \"That will be 94 essences, please.\" And the man reached into his pocket and pulled out the exact number for payment. The next day, the man and the ostrich came again and the man said..','2016-12-16 17:02:52'),(10730592,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Kinesis | Learn',0,47,3,3719,1148,'Although the production of elements is unconscious and constant by al dreamers, it is not only focal energy. Elements carries with it the desires and emotions of the one who deploys it, which is what allows for elements to have incredible versatility to those who develop their skill at using it. Learn this art\'s history and tell me how powerful emotions can be. Also, learn this arts basics. ','2016-12-17 08:47:33'),(10730241,2483554788,3070,637534208,43,'Purify | Learn',0,47,3,3647,1150,'Purify is a rather exhausting art. It costs a whopping 15 Resilience. What a cheat! With you being second sphere, thats\'s nearly all of the resilience you have! Offer a few dreamers this curse-vaxation for a small fee of a talisman in return. Insist and remind them of the importance of their annual Curse Vaxines. That they are months behind schedule. Take note of their reactions. Also, tell me if plateauing this art has any benefits. ','2016-12-17 07:36:46'),(10730205,2483554788,3070,637534208,43,'Restore | Learn',0,47,3,3600,1215,'Plane beautification and varied spatial positions and sensations of colors in the dreamstate create visual contrasts which contribute to the aesthetic development. DreamWright masters used this perception of the dynamics of color to give considerable character to these environments. Journey to one of the undesirable, unappealing areas and use your imagination to add to this room\'s chroma value. -Restore- life into this room. Additionally, tell me how much DreamSoul is healed per plateau up to second plat. ','2016-12-17 07:27:16'),(10736771,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'Shatter | Learn',0,47,3,3771,1200,'The key to shattering is knowing the anatomy of a ward. First evoke a ward and take some time to examine every detail you can about the ward. Following that, gather the ideas of 1 other dreamer. Combine those with your own. Then tell me how think Willpower interacts with everything. Also, tell me the basics of the art. ','2016-12-18 05:57:23'),(10835130,526824,5704514,704643072,2803495,'Corr Mini 10',0,47,11,5689,4307,'Ensure that the new arts are being tasked for, I have slacked dont let me continue','2016-12-30 01:24:28'),(10735896,4485,13437953,0,0,'KoES Flag',0,24,11,552,-12020,'','2016-12-18 02:53:27'),(10736865,872942052,3070,637534208,43,'FlameShaft | Learn',0,47,3,3706,1148,'Fire is a recurring symbol in the dream as of lately. There have been countless omens of a coming darkness. Enlist the aid of another dreamer to create an object in which you could vanquish a living darkness. Your report will consist of convincing me of its efficiency. Additionally, learn the damage per plateau up to 5th plat. ','2016-12-18 06:09:33'),(10735962,57381,13437953,0,0,'Soul of Flames',0,24,12,219,-15131,'The movements of this flame seem almost... alive.  The sound of breathing can be heard.','2016-12-18 03:08:18'),(10734510,57349,13437953,0,0,'Torch',0,24,30,-3105,-1546,'','2016-12-17 22:31:38'),(10735961,130041,17171711,0,0,'Shadowed Gem',0,22,22,-10250,-7909,'A solid black gem.  It is cold to the touch.  Shadows hang to it like a thick fog.','2016-12-18 03:07:02'),(10793435,4261939684,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop: The Art',0,47,3,3649,1026,'Eavesdrop is a FateSender Major art. It costs 40 Lucidity. It is acquired at Orbit 70. Affected: Evoker Duration: 1 Minute + 1 per plateau Description: This art a dreamer to hear the says in adjacent room. This is done by selecting a portal similar to Ward to listen in on. You hear a percentage of every say in the room depending on the level. (i.e. Level 10 = 10%) Plateau Effect: The evoke time decreases and duration of the effect increases. ','2016-12-24 23:06:55'),(10745634,3876063716,9178110,4160749568,2566951,'LadySilver - Sns Da',0,47,11,5922,4158,'What nightmares haunt us in our waking? I\'d like for you to discover this for me! Learn about a few dreamers and discover what haunts them on their shards. Tell me what you learned! You know the deal. \r\n','2016-12-18 23:25:00'),(10818738,4026536613,13437953,0,0,'Fighting Policy',0,41,1,459,-797,'There will be NO fighting in the Library, Teaching Guild or the adjacent halls. If you are found to be in violation of this policy, you will be placed on a train ban for a specific amount of time. Should further violations occur during this time, stronger action will be taken. Escalating arguments will not be tolerated while teaching is occurring. You will be asked to leave the area.               **HeadMaster Akkadian**','2016-12-28 04:16:27'),(10753349,60613,13437953,0,0,'Lightning',0,39,25,-184,-2661,'','2016-12-19 18:36:10'),(10753787,3758623208,2824,721420288,39,'Milk & Cookies',0,47,2,-3348,-61,'Magical it is as well. The dream knows your favrotie type of milk and the cookies you dream of. Enjoy you deserve a treat!','2016-12-19 19:32:29'),(10753348,60613,13437953,0,0,'Lightning',0,39,25,-287,-2932,'','2016-12-19 18:36:10'),(10754032,3758623208,2825,721420288,39,'Milk & Cookies',0,41,14,6007,-3202,'Magical it is as well. The dream knows your favrotie type of milk and the cookies you dream of. Enjoy you deserve a treat!','2016-12-19 20:07:59'),(10754029,3758623208,2826,721420288,39,'Milk & Cookies',0,41,8,275,-9830,'Magical it is as well. The dream knows your favrotie type of milk and the cookies you dream of. Enjoy you deserve a treat!','2016-12-19 20:06:44'),(10755300,526867,3890741505,1499158,1537792,'Ward',0,24,30,-5166,-1697,'','2016-12-20 00:45:19'),(10753820,3758623208,2825,721420288,39,'Milk and Cookies',0,3,29,-10119,4372,'Magical it is as well. The dream knows your favrotie type of milk and the cookies you dream of. Enjoy you deserve a treat!','2016-12-19 19:33:28'),(10754026,3758623208,2823,721420288,39,'Milk & Cookies',0,41,2,416,-3320,'Magical it is as well. The dream knows your favrotie type of milk and the cookies you dream of. Enjoy you deserve a treat!','2016-12-19 20:05:46'),(10755334,526867,3387425025,119297,1537792,'Ward',0,24,2,-384,-2339,'','2016-12-20 00:49:38'),(10757301,2835876324,3476478,4026531840,2565672,'Train 80',0,47,9,-4742,4097,'As you are progressing as a dual focus teacher, what advise would you give to teachers who are ready to take the next step at the end of their 8th sphere. What should they focus on? **A**','2016-12-20 06:41:11'),(10757207,2835876324,265214,4026531840,2565672,'SoulMaster 80',0,47,9,-4724,4097,'I wish for you to find strengths and weaknesses for all of the focii. Be detailed in your research and reporting. Ask someone you think to be intelligent to make a list as well and share with me. **A**','2016-12-20 06:27:05'),(10761776,34081252,9571326,1191182336,2579752,'RallyL-Tembs',0,18,31,16550,-6296,'Ask around and find out three ways people have used rally that made them just LOVE the art. Then come up with one way of your own that you would use it that would be all your own. Also, why do you think this is a guardian art and everyone cant learn it?\r\n','2016-12-20 21:30:52'),(10793624,3725068772,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop: Theory',0,47,3,3714,1024,'Eavesdrop uses both the properties of Insight and Lucidity to manipulate sound. First the FateSender must materialize two FateSender crystals, one in the target room and another in the FateSender\'s possession. Following that, Lucidity must be channeled into the threads of lucidity into the portal to make a connection between the two crystals. Subsequently while this is being accomplished, insight must flow through the connection to both conceal the crystals and allow for the flowing of sound to be heard. ','2016-12-24 23:47:27'),(12719068,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,44,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:22'),(12719067,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,44,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:18:22'),(10788612,3557296612,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | Learn',0,47,3,3776,1083,'There has always been an issue with sensitive information in the dream. Some things are best kept in secret. Oftentimes, improper use of this information has lead to home closures, dreamer embarassment, and even put others in danger. Contemplate on all of the conversations you\'ve had in past, present, and future. Also, look at some of the history and develop an argument on what type of information was better left unsaid. Ensure a thorough arugment. Also, learn the basics of this art. ','2016-12-24 07:39:17'),(10776175,17304036,3070,3456106496,42,'Combine Please!',0,17,19,16515,433,'Please combine these items!  Thank you!  ~Snow Angel~','2016-12-22 14:37:42'),(12718153,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,21,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:59'),(10776487,520096613,13437953,0,0,'Conciousness',0,48,2,-1115,517,'','2016-12-22 15:46:21'),(10778227,526820,3070,1191182336,40,'ProsCons 2',0,47,9,-4742,4081,'Pros: Self sufficient (recharge/combine), only ones with vision, blend, blast, ele perk.\r\nCons: Cant forge invis, invis is pretty useless.SM\r\nPros: Poison/antidote, restore, trap. Cons: Arts are outwardly focused (support), get trapped by wards.','2016-12-22 21:13:33'),(10778228,526820,3070,1191182336,40,'ProsCons',0,47,9,-4724,4079,'FS Pros: Get on peoples nerves, makes people more suseptible to damage, lots of mass arts, if opponent isnt wearing protective arts = screwed, bleeding effect with razorwind.\r\nCons: Lots of tasks, all arts are outwardly focused (Nothing beneficial to them), get trapped with wards.  GK\r\nPros: Return, reflect, can ward people in/shatter, GK bonus, protective arts +20.\r\nCons: Usually stupid, rely on chaks since they dont have a offensive arts and they cant recharge their chaks.  DS','2016-12-22 21:15:13'),(10778730,3557296612,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | Learn',0,47,3,3825,1086,'Sound waves need to travel through a medium such as solid, liquid or gas. The sound waves move through each of these mediums by vibrating the entire object. But do these ideas apply for the DreamState? I mean we have these elements but do they work in the same manner. Prepare some arguments taking your position on the nature of sound in the dream. Prepare to be challenged by me. Good luck!','2016-12-22 22:49:25'),(12718152,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,21,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:59'),(10779010,3557296612,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | Learn',0,47,3,3807,1087,'Take up a group of dreamers and have them evoke Inscribe. The instruct them to write down every art you evoke in quick succession. Make you sure you make note of what order you evoked you arts in. Do it very quickly and try to decieve followers. Make this game even more challenging by doing fake out on arts by cancelling. Have fun!','2016-12-22 23:44:29'),(10788489,3557296612,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | Learn',0,47,3,3761,1084,'The life of a spy. Use your imagination to create detailed imagery, experiences on a imagined life of a spy. If you run out of inspiration, find a friend and act out as a spy. The method you choose to write express this out is your choice (Play, Inscription, Story telling) Additionally, learn the basics of this art. Have fun!','2016-12-24 07:21:36'),(10793153,4094167524,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 20',0,47,3,3639,1082,'Experiments provide for a simple and engaging framework for familiarizing dreamers with the process of quantitative social research. Eavesdrop is a relatively new art ripe for many experiments. Devise methodation on how this specific experimentation plan can serve as a model for more complex and rigorous art creations in the future. ','2016-12-24 22:17:38'),(10788949,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 10',0,47,3,3687,1081,'Fashion of a spy. Every super sleuth needs eyes in the back of their head. GIven your well known status as dreamer fashionita, I would like for you to design a spy suit containing the following items: Overcoat, glasses, boots, and a spy gagdet of choice. You can\'t spy if you ain\'t cute! Add other items, if you so desire.','2016-12-24 08:25:54'),(10788991,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 10 ',0,47,3,3744,1084,'The dream of the shadows. There are a few contreversial dreamers in the dream who\'ve acquired the abilty to do things in the dark. One dreamer who comes of note is that of the dreamer Harkyn. Ask around and learn of the things he\'s been able to achieve and develop countermethods to his ways. Share this with at least one of his adversaries.','2016-12-24 08:34:50'),(10788720,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 10 ',0,47,3,3730,1087,'Spying can help you uncover the deepest, darkest secrets of the people around you, whether they are strangers or your master teacher. Make a few attempts to eavesdrop into the private conversations of areas inaccessible to you (Teacher halls, higher sphered areas, house meetings). Take note of every method to remain inconspicuous. Be careful and don\'t be a jerk! ','2016-12-24 07:48:54'),(10788796,3825732068,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 10',0,47,3,3701,1083,'Death by habit. We have a certain few dreamers who go through the same motions every single dream. Habits like this are extremely easy to be manipulated. Study one of these habitual groups of dreamers and follow through with an eavesdrop and for one minute take down every word said. Take this information and show them the dangers of habit by repeating their conversation. Good luck. ','2016-12-24 08:08:38'),(10788992,4094167524,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 20',0,47,3,3656,1086,'Detective Memory. Ring out a full array of items and put these objects on a table. Use items that a spy might use: spy lens, duster, passport, codex copier, etc. Allow dreamers 10 seconds to view them. When the time is up, take the items and have each dreamer describe them to the best of their abilities. Give the dreamers 5 minutes to write everything that they remember and whomever remembers the most is the winner. Have fun!','2016-12-24 08:40:39'),(10793278,4094167524,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 20',0,47,3,3622,1081,'Cipher codes are encoded messages whereas each letter is replaced with another letter or symbol. By utilizing the Cipher decoder I\'ve given you, Decode the following message: Zheo ha neeiijd. Then encode a message in response to me. Then, create your own cipher code and have another dreamer decode it. ','2016-12-24 22:35:19'),(12718151,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,21,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:59'),(10793341,4094167524,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 20',0,47,3,3604,1080,'Act out a dream as a spy. Be sure to play the part exceptionally well. Use Forge, Inscribe, and mission boards to add to the part. Choose a dreamer to act as an enemy and attempt to get them to play along. The both of you will try to undermine the other\'s efforts in the dark until the final moment of conflict. At this point you will fight each other by utilzing your spy tools! The loser will have to surrender and tell 4 dreamers a lengthy report on their failure. Have fun!','2016-12-24 22:48:49'),(10795816,1678248420,3070,637534208,43,'Know | 10',0,47,3,3463,1086,'Knowledge of the dream is characterized by awarenes or familiarity gained by experience of a fact or opinion of an area. Our dream has many areas which have detailed descriptions but lack any signifiicant knowledge. Spend a few hours areas through a commonly used area with a know description and take note of who passes through and what is said. Detail this on a codex to be turned in to me. ','2016-12-25 06:14:21'),(10795848,1409812964,3070,637534208,43,'Know | 20',0,47,3,3447,1086,'Every single area in the dream is rich with some sort of history. Ask 2 dreamers to follow you to an obscure area of choice. Ask them about memories about a room. What did you find out about this area? How does this relate to the history of the dream?','2016-12-25 06:19:36'),(10793121,4094167524,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop | 20',0,47,3,3672,1084,'Among the dream are many hints of knowledge. Information around the dream that gives subtle hints at the make up of the dream. Utilize Know, Room names, history and whatever else to argue the reality of either FreeSoul or Illuminate beliefs. Learn to listen to the enviornment. ','2016-12-24 22:06:40'),(10793656,3456633316,3070,637534208,43,'Eavesdrop: FateSeer',0,47,3,3784,1025,'It is my thought that we could introduce dual focus specific arts. This art could be exclusive to the FateSeer. At an elemental level this art does indeed utilize both properties of Insight and Lucidity. It requires a mastery of both elemental forces. This also motivates dreamers to work towards getting their second focii for the sake of discovery of new skillsets and abilties. ','2016-12-24 23:56:08'),(10795784,1946683876,3070,637534208,43,'Know: Improvements',0,47,3,3453,1041,'Know is an art which allows for known information about the room by deriving locate dreamer to its rawest insightful form. This ability can be improved to allow for more information about the room\'s recent past time. For instance, a drastic improvement could be to use for having additional facts about the room like actions performed by dreamers, words said, and the direction non-mind blanked dreamers have went, etc. With plateau, more important facts from a database could be listed. 9th could be editting. ','2016-12-25 06:04:33'),(12718150,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,21,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:59'),(10804236,319293924,3070,637534208,43,'Amulet: Improvement',0,47,3,3690,1211,'Amulet is never used or given out due to its permanence. Almost always it is destroyed nearly right after due to this. My proposed change is to make a charge based amulet system. Unplatted Amulet would have 10 charges and subtract all the way down to 1 charge at 9th plateau. This would also make newlies who don\'t know better less at risk for using one. ','2016-12-26 05:39:42'),(10809320,1074268644,1707006,2046820352,2562346,'Reweave30 | Dreiko',0,41,23,-3143,2977,'Weave together an 2 idea or 2 items. Have someone who is NOT a Soul Master destroy these ideas or items.  Now have them reweave them, once again. Tell me how they did things differently than you would have, and explain how your focus is more successful than theirs. ','2016-12-26 22:59:29'),(12718149,0,0,0,0,'level item',0,21,0,0,0,NULL,'2017-09-28 17:17:59'),(10819156,252185064,2842,922746880,43,'Vision 2 sideways 8',0,21,16,-2784,-3061,'In north and south outer gate of harrows lie pits of utter darkness. You can observe a shamblix falling into them, and even hear their cries and they can curse you from there. If you join them in said pit though they won\'t attack.. why is this ? Where do they go ? where do YOU go ? I look forward to your report. ','2016-12-28 05:48:24'),(10817316,4144499172,2427902,1392508928,2579751,'DreamBlade 60',0,18,31,16569,-6372,'I would like for you to come up with at least 6 prototype blades and show them to me. They can be for ceremonial use, or have a super hard blade for crafting, maybe one for slicing faces off or just a real cool cheese knife. You choose. <T>','2016-12-27 23:52:51'),(10817187,4144499172,5704702,1392508928,2562343,'Dazzle Support',0,41,23,-3056,2494,'Tell me who needs to work on their Dazzle and how we can get them tasks 